<h2><strong>Harry’s Marketing: 5 Must-Know Strategies You Need to Steal</strong></h2>



<p>I recommend reading this article from beginning to end (preferably with a nice warm cup of coffee).&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But if you’re pressed for time, and eager to dive in, click a link below to jump to a strategy of interest (Strategy #5, particularly Email #3, is genius):<br></p>



<p><a href="#1">1. Create Brand Advocates with 3 Emotionally-Driven Story Archetypes</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Win New Business with This Replicable Word-of-Mouth Referral Engine</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Build White Hot, White Hat Backlinks with These 3 E-Commerce Link Building Tactics</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Convert On-The-Fence Buyers with These 3 Proven Ad Angles</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Engage Subscribers and Increase Average Order Value (AOV) with “The CPS Method”</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Create Brand Advocates with 2 Emotionally-Driven Story Archetypes</strong></h2>



<p>Harry’s leverages two classic <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/story-based-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">storytelling</a> archetypes in their marketing:<br></p>



<ol><li>The welcomed prophet</li><li>The scrappy underdog</li></ol>



<p>Let’s look at each in detail.</p>



<h3>Story Archetype #1: The Welcomed Prophet</h3>



<p>Beginning with their about page (appropriately named “Our Story”), Harry’s position themselves as a remedy to a problem that’s plagued men for decades: overly-expensive razor blades.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="350" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-1024x350.png" alt="The Company That_s Fixing Shaving" class="wp-image-79285" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-1024x350.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-300x102.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-768x262.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-380x130.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-600x205.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-760x259.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-103x35.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-146x50.png 146w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-740x253.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-220x75.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-385x131.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Further, they define what they do, who they do it for, and further down, why they do what they do. Your Why, the reason you do what you do, is essential. <a href="https://www.ted.com/talks/simon_sinek_how_great_leaders_inspire_action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">As Simon Sinek says</a>, “People don’t buy what you do; they buy why you do it.”<br></p>



<p>Without their Why, Harry’s are another “me-too” online retailer looking to make a fast buck from a lucrative industry. But with it, they’re a voice for the everyman, a cause worth getting behind (more on that in a moment).&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>What’s interesting is, if you look hard enough, you realize Harry’s brand themselves as, what copywriter Dan Kennedy calls, “a welcomed prophet.”&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Put it this way: people know razor blades are expensive. They always have. And they always will. Yet few companies rose to the occasion and explicitly referenced it in their marketing.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Harry’s know <strong>good marketing is a result of saying things to buyers that reinforce and confirm what they </strong><strong><em>already</em></strong><strong> believe.</strong>&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Unsurprisingly, it’s an archetype that resonates with their audience on an emotional level. So much so, that Harry’s have been able to get 324 backlinks to their about page alone:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="207" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-1024x207.png" alt="324 Backlinks" class="wp-image-79153" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-1024x207.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-300x61.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-768x155.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-380x77.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-600x121.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-760x154.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-173x35.png 173w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-247x50.png 247w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-740x150.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-220x44.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks-385x78.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/324-Backlinks.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item.</strong> Ask yourself, “What do people believe—specifically—that I can show up and agree with, so you can sell to them?” Then, put your answer in your marketing.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For example, if you sell women’s clothes, you can address the overwhelm and inconvenience that comes from clothes shopping (<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.trunkclub.com/" target="_blank">TrunkClub</a> does a superb job of this on <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.trunkclub.com/about" target="_blank">their about page</a>).&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h3>Story Archetype #2: The Scrappy Underdog</h3>



<p>When Harry’s launched in 2013, they entered a heavily-dominated industry with Gillette owning 66.3% of the market share:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="282" height="460" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gilette-Market-Share.png" alt="Gilette Market Share" class="wp-image-79197" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gilette-Market-Share.png 282w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gilette-Market-Share-184x300.png 184w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gilette-Market-Share-21x35.png 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gilette-Market-Share-31x50.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gilette-Market-Share-220x359.png 220w" sizes="(max-width: 282px) 100vw, 282px" /></figure></div>



<p>In the beginning, Harry’s were up against what many considered an insurmountable challenge. But Harry’s accepted and assumed the role of David to Gillette’s Goliath—and they ran with it.<br></p>



<p>You can see it in their “infomercial” below, referencing Gillette as “Big Razor Company”:<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe title="Harry&#039;s - Meet the Shaving Company That&#039;s Fixing Shaving [FULL LENGTH]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eYWCUGmGuss?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>Harry’s role as “the scrappy underdog” isn’t anything new; companies have played that role for as long as the archetype has had a name. But what’s interesting about Harry’s approach is threefold.<br></p>



<p>First, it’s consistent throughout <em>their</em> marketing. You see this from their ads to their alternative pages:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1010" height="289" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette.png" alt="Harrs Versus Gilette" class="wp-image-79201" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette.png 1010w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-300x86.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-768x220.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-380x109.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-600x172.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-760x217.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-122x35.png 122w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-175x50.png 175w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-740x212.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-220x63.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harrs-Versus-Gilette-385x110.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1010px) 100vw, 1010px" /></figure></div>



<p>Second, it’s <em>reaffirmed</em> by fans in YouTube or Facebook comments:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="635" height="215" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment.png" alt="YouTube Comment" class="wp-image-79309" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment.png 635w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-300x102.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-380x129.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-600x203.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-103x35.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-148x50.png 148w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-220x74.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/YouTube-Comment-385x130.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px" /></figure></div>



<p>Third, it’s reinforced <em>elsewhere</em> when they’re covered by media outlets like <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/stevenbertoni/2015/07/07/razor-wars-harrys-raises-75-million-to-fight-gillette-and-dollar-shave-club/#177fc8d3590c" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Forbes</a> and <a href="https://www.marketingweek.com/2017/07/31/harrys-shaving-disrupt-uk-market/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Marketing Week</a> (after all, it’s a great angle for a story):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="447" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-1024x447.png" alt="Blog Post Gillette" class="wp-image-79233" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-1024x447.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-768x335.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-600x262.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-760x331.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-740x323.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image28.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>We love stories of heroism. But we especially love rooting for the underdog. They’re an ordinary person—just like you—and they’re worth investing in.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Inviting customers to invest in you emotionally, when appropriate, gives you an advantage of your competitors. If, say, your “Big Razor Company” tries to undercut you on price (<a href="http://fortune.com/2017/11/29/gillette-blades-dollar-shave-club-harrys/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">like Gillette tried recently with their “cheaper” blades</a>), your customers will stay with you. Why? Because if they’re a part of something greater than themselves, they’re invested in <em>you</em> before the brand.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Like many products, razor blades are a commodity that you can buy at a cheap price. But, once a customer has invested in your brand, they remain loyal (providing you continue nurturing that relationship) and are willing to pay premium price.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="755" height="349" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment.png" alt="Facebook Comment" class="wp-image-79189" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment.png 755w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-600x277.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-740x342.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Comment-385x178.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 755px) 100vw, 755px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item: </strong>Brand advocates are essential in today’s economy, so give customers a reason to invest in you emotionally using story archetypes. You don’t have to use the ones listed above; there are countless story archetypes to choose from.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what’s most important is to have your story consistent throughout your marketing. You want to remind people <em>why</em> you’re worth investing in and being a part of.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Win New Business with This Replicable Word-of-Mouth Referral Engine&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re like most business owners, you know the importance of <a href="https://referralrock.com/blog/referral-programs-101-everything-you-need-to-build-a-referral-marketing-program/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">referral marketing</a>. But few build a predictable and repeatable referral system into their marketing.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And the numbers couldn’t be more revealing.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.referralcandy.com/blog/referral-marketing-awesome-infographic/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">According to ReferralCandy</a>, <strong>83% of satisfied customers are willing to refer products and services. </strong>So far, so good.<strong> </strong>Yet, <strong>only 29% actually do.</strong><br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="548" height="415" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t.png" alt="Sadly Most Don_t" class="wp-image-79261" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t.png 548w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t-300x227.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t-380x288.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t-66x50.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t-220x167.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sadly-Most-Don_t-385x292.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px" /></figure></div>



<p>Harry’s knows this better than anyone. From day one, they built a fully-automated word-of-mouth referral engine—before they even had a single customer.<br></p>



<p>And the results were remarkable.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>One week before their e-commerce site went live, Harry’s acquired 100,000 emails addresses through a week-long pre-launch campaign.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>“The idea for our campaign was built around our belief that the most powerful and effective way to be introduced to our new company was through a credible referral,” <a href="https://tim.blog/2014/07/21/harrys-prelaunchr-email/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">writes Co-Founder and CEO Jeff Raider</a>. “Thus, <strong>we focused on building a campaign that helped people to spread the word to their friends</strong>.”<br></p>



<p>Below is how their campaign works. Model it. You might not get 100,000 email addresses, but you will skyrocket your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">list building</a> efforts.<br></p>



<h3>Step 1: Use Email Outreach to Notify Your Friends and Family</h3>



<p>Harry’s had just 12 employees in the beginning. Twelve. That’s it. Now imagine going from 12 email addresses to 100,000 in one week. Impressive, isn’t it?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Each employee wrote a personal email to everyone in their network notifying them of the launch and inviting them to opt in on a landing page (more on that below).<br></p>



<h3>Step 2: Drive Traffic to a Dedicated Landing Page</h3>



<p>On the homepage, Harry’s invited users to leave their email address to get notified of the site’s launch:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="467" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-1024x467.png" alt="Be The First to Know" class="wp-image-79161" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-1024x467.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-300x137.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-768x351.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-380x173.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-600x274.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-760x347.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-77x35.png 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-110x50.png 110w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-740x338.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-220x100.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know-385x176.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Be-The-First-to-Know.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>(Harry’s cryptic headline urged users to opt in to learn more.)</em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>A clear design with a curiosity-driven headline. Nothing new there. But here’s where it gets interesting…<br></p>



<h3>Step 3: Invite Users to Share on Social (with a Twist)</h3>



<p>After opting in, Harry’s invited users to refer others on social in exchange for freebies:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="588" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-1024x588.png" alt="Invite Friends _ Earn Products" class="wp-image-79237" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-1024x588.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-300x172.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-768x441.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-380x218.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-600x345.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-760x437.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-87x50.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-740x425.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-220x126.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products-385x221.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Invite-Friends-_-Earn-Products.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And that’s not all…<br></p>



<p>The more friends user referred, the better the prizes they won. For instance, if they signed up five friends, they won a free shave cream. Not bad for a few minutes of work. But if they referred 50 friends, they won the grand prize: a year of free shaving.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>“We wanted the entire experience to feel like a fun game.” <a href="https://tim.blog/2014/07/21/harrys-prelaunchr-email/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">writes Raider</a>. “We heard from some friends that they took the referral campaign like a personal challenge.”<br></p>



<p>And that they did:<br></p>



<p><strong>A whopping 77% of the emails came from referrals, meaning around 20,000 people referred around 65,000 friends.</strong><br></p>



<p>We only want to refer others to offers that are interesting and make us look good. So, while it’s unlikely all 65,000 subscribers were relevant, it’s safe to assume a fair percentage were, giving Harry’s a highly-targeted list of prospects before even opening for business.<br></p>



<h3>Step 4: Use Software to Safeguard Yourself Against Fraud</h3>



<p>Not everyone, of course, is honest. Few will take advantage given the opportunity. Using <a href="https://sendgrid.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SendGrid</a>, Harry’s sent an email to every email address entered. If that email bounced, SendGrid interpreted the email address as illegitimate and removed it from the contest.<br></p>



<p>Four years after Harry’s launch, referrals continue to be a big part of their traffic share, with 220,000 sessions in the past three months alone (as of writing):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="256" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-1024x256.png" alt="Total Referals" class="wp-image-79301" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-1024x256.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-300x75.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-768x192.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-380x95.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-600x150.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-760x190.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-140x35.png 140w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-200x50.png 200w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-740x185.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-220x55.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals-385x96.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Total-Referals.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item:</strong> It’s tempting to believe a large audience necessitates virality. But, as we’ve seen, even a few referrals can compound exponentially.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>If you’re launching a new product/service, or looking to reach new audiences, use software like <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://kickofflabs.com/" target="_blank">KickOffLabs</a> to create a viral campaign. Offer freebies in exchange for referrals and above all, make it super simple for users to share.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Build White Hot, White Hat Backlinks with These 3 E-Commerce Link Building Tactics</strong></h2>



<p>Before moving forward with this section, we need to address the elephant in the room.<br></p>



<p>Harry’s have acquired a TON of backlinks from the press. Their meteoric rise has featured in countless high-authority sites including <em>The New York Times</em>, <em>The Guardian</em>, and <em>Forbes:</em><br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="830" height="452" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks.png" alt="Harry_s Backlinks" class="wp-image-79205" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks.png 830w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-300x163.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-768x418.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-380x207.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-600x327.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-760x414.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-740x403.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Backlinks-385x210.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px" /></figure></div>



<p>Writing you can achieve similar results would insult your intelligence. I am NOT going to do that. But what I am going to do is show you three untapped link-building strategies Harry’s used that you can, too.<br></p>



<p>These include:<br></p>



<ol><li>The Best-Of Backlink Builder</li><li>The Poster Boy Formula&nbsp;</li><li>The Marketer Magnet</li></ol>



<p>Let’s discuss each, step-by-step.<br></p>



<h3>Link Building Strategy #1: The Best-Of Backlink Builder</h3>



<p>A common search query for customers at the consideration stage of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">the buyer’s journey</a> is “best [blank] for [blank].” Harry’s is a subscription box service mainly for men. Here’s what I found when I searched for “best subscription box services for men”:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="910" height="445" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018.png" alt="Best Subscription Boxes for Men 2018" class="wp-image-79165" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018.png 910w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-768x376.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-380x186.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-600x293.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-760x372.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-740x362.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-for-Men-2018-385x188.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 910px) 100vw, 910px" /></figure></div>



<p>Google delivered 6,560 search results for that exact phrase. Impressive.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.purewow.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">PureWow</a> is one example of a site that featured Harry’s in a best-of article called “<a href="https://www.purewow.com/home/best-subscription-boxes-for-everyone/slide12" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">The 50 Best Subscription Boxes</a>”:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="447" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-1024x447.png" alt="Best Subscription Boxes" class="wp-image-79169" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-1024x447.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-768x335.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-600x262.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-760x331.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-740x323.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Subscription-Boxes.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This one article earned them a nice link from a site with a <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/dr-score/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">domain rating</a> score of 77:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="830" height="140" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77.png" alt="Zendesk DR77" class="wp-image-79313" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77.png 830w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-300x51.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-768x130.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-380x64.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-600x101.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-760x128.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-180x30.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-250x42.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-740x125.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-220x37.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Zendesk-DR77-385x65.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px" /></figure></div>



<p>Whether Harry’s marketing department reached out for this link is irrelevant: You don’t need to wait for sites to link to you; you need to reach out and ask.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how to do that.<br></p>



<p>First, run a search for “best [blank] for [blank].” For example, if you sell women’s yoga pants, you might search for “best yoga pants for women” (I recommend adding “+ [current year]” for up-to-date content):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="685" height="435" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1.png" alt="Best Yoga Pants for Women" class="wp-image-79177" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1.png 685w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-300x191.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-380x241.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-600x381.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-220x140.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-1-385x244.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 685px) 100vw, 685px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you want to go one step further, you can add + [competitor] to the search operator:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="810" height="100" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018.png" alt="Best Yoga Pants for Women 2018" class="wp-image-79173" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018.png 810w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-300x37.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-768x95.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-380x47.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-600x74.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-760x94.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-180x22.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-250x31.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-740x91.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-220x27.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-2018-385x48.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px" /></figure></div>



<p>You can even go to ‘Tools &gt; Past Week” to get recent results (this makes link building easier):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="680" height="100" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week.png" alt="Past Week" class="wp-image-79253" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week.png 680w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-380x56.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-600x88.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-180x26.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-220x32.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Past-Week-385x57.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure></div>



<p>Check each site’s DR and add any sites with an identical DR to your site (or higher) to a spreadsheet. Then, reach out to them asking them if they would consider adding your site to their list. Yes, it’s time-consuming. But it works.<br></p>



<h3>Link Building Strategy #2: The “Posterboy Formula”</h3>



<p>Coined by <a href="https://videofruit.com/blog/poster-boy/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Bryan Harris,</a> the “Posterboy Formula” involves writing a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer testimonial</a> in exchange for a link to your site.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it works:<br></p>



<ol><li>Choose a company with an audience like yours</li><li>Buy one of their products</li><li>Notify the company specifying the results you achieved&nbsp;</li><li>Offer to write a case study</li></ol>



<p>No one is exempt from using the “Posterboy Formula”. In fact, Harry’s got a juicy 92DR link from <a href="https://www.zendesk.com/blog/harrys/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">ZenDesk</a> after writing a case study on how they deliver effortless customer service:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="447" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-1024x447.png" alt="Harry_s on Zen Desk" class="wp-image-79209" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-1024x447.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-768x335.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-600x262.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-760x331.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-740x323.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-on-Zen-Desk.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h3>Link Building Strategy #3: The Marketer Magnet Method</h3>



<p>No matter what industry you’re in, marketing blogs always want unique marketing examples for their content.<br></p>



<p>Take our article on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">abandonment cart emails</a>, for instance.<br></p>



<p>We wanted to go above and beyond with that post, so we abandoned dozens of checkouts to get great email examples.<br></p>



<p>When we included a site’s email in our article, we linked to them. But we also got links to <em>our</em> content from other blogs because our examples weren’t available elsewhere.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s a link we got from <a href="https://neilpatel.com/blog/clickable-email-subject-line-types/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Neil Patel’s blog</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="810" height="626" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel.png" alt="Link from Neil Patel" class="wp-image-79241" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel.png 810w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-300x232.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-768x594.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-380x294.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-600x464.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-760x587.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-65x50.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-634x490.png 634w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-220x170.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-from-Neil-Patel-385x298.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px" /></figure></div>



<p>Win. Win.<br></p>



<p>Harry’s knows this better than anyone. They have countless examples of good marketing to link to and feature. (I wouldn’t be writing this article otherwise, right?).<br></p>



<p>From their about page to their Facebook ads to their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email marketing</a>, Harry’s give marketing blogs never-ending fodder for their content.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Here’s an example of <a href="https://blog.kissmetrics.com/a-great-support-portal/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Kissmetrics</a> praising Harry’s customer support portal:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="670" height="545" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You.png" alt="Tell Customers The Best Way to Reach You" class="wp-image-79281" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You.png 670w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-300x244.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-380x309.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-600x488.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-43x35.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-61x50.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-602x490.png 602w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-220x179.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tell-Customers-The-Best-Way-to-Reach-You-385x313.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item.</strong> To create content that’s a marketer magnet, go above and beyond in your marketing. Ask yourself, “What can I do differently that will give marketing blogs a reason to feature me in their content?”&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Like many link-building strategies, The Marketer Magnet is HARD. You will need to do a TON of email outreach and you won’t get many replies. But it does work and it’s worth the organic traffic that comes from the effort.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Convert On-The-Fence Buyers with These 3 Proven Ad Angles&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Facebook Advertising is a double-edged sword for many marketers.<br></p>



<p>On the one hand, done right, it’s a predictable and repeatable acquisition channel. Cash goes in. Profit comes out. By contrast, it’s a constant source of frustration for even seasoned professionals.<br></p>



<p>Harry’s mitigate the above by focusing on three tried-and-tested ad angles:<br></p>



<ol><li>Positioning</li><li>Objection handling</li><li>Damage mitigation</li></ol>



<h3>Ad #1. Positioning</h3>



<p>As mentioned before, Harry’s position themselves as “the company that’s fixing shaving.”<br></p>



<p>One thing to note about Harry’s marketing is that their storytelling runs throughout their advertising. From their about page to their Facebook Ads and everywhere in-between, Harry’s reinforce their buyer person’s pain (expensive razor blade) and position themselves as the solution (custom-made razor blade at affordable prices).<br></p>



<p>In one ad, they introduce the problem:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="620" height="675" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad.png" alt="Harry_s Positioning Ad" class="wp-image-79213" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad.png 620w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-276x300.png 276w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-380x414.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-600x653.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-46x50.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-450x490.png 450w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-220x240.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Positioning-Ad-385x419.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Source: <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://adespresso.com/ad/1177440/" target="_blank">AdEspresso</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>When users click through, they’re directed to a landing page where they’re offered an immediate solution:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="461" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-1024x461.png" alt="Try The Company That_s Fixing Shaving" class="wp-image-79305" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-1024x461.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-768x345.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving-385x173.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Try-The-Company-That_s-Fixing-Shaving.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>From there, Harry’s offers users a chance to begin a free trial. If they don’t convert, there’s an opportunity to retarget them with the below ad&#8230;</p>



<h3>Ad #2. Objection Handling</h3>



<p>This ad works well with a cart recovery email (see: Strategy #5).<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it works:<br></p>



<p>A user visits Harry’s site either through search or clicking an ad like the one above. They reach a product page or even checkout page, but they leave their site before completing their order. They showed interest, but <em>something</em> prevented them from moving forward.<br></p>



<p>Later, they see an ad like the one below:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="620" height="665" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced.png" alt="Still Not Convinced" class="wp-image-79273" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced.png 620w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-280x300.png 280w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-380x408.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-600x644.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-47x50.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-457x490.png 457w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-220x236.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Not-Convinced-385x413.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Source: <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://adespresso.com/ad/1179258/" target="_blank">AdEspresso</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>A retargeting ad like the above works well for three key reasons:<br></p>



<ol><li><strong>It’s personalized.</strong> It addresses the fact that the reader is already thinking about buying. The user visited the site before, but something prevented them from moving forward.</li><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><strong>It focuses on benefits over features</strong></a><strong>.</strong> Harry’s customer-centric copy focuses on what the reader stands to gain from taking action.</li><li><strong>It offers an ironclad guarantee.</strong> No one wants to commit to something they might not want later. Harry’s knows this. So they offer a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/satisfaction-guarantees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">guarantee</a> customers love (and competitors hate).&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol>



<p>Beyond Facebook, this ad was consistent as a display ad as well, showing up on several websites users browsed later:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="734" height="98" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor.png" alt="Still Want to Try This Razor" class="wp-image-79277" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor.png 734w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-300x40.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-380x51.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-600x80.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-180x24.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-250x33.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-220x29.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Still-Want-to-Try-This-Razor-385x51.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 734px) 100vw, 734px" /></figure></div>



<p>If users don’t return to their site, there’s one more opportunity to convert them&#8230;<br></p>



<h3>Ad #3. Damage Mitigation&nbsp;</h3>



<p>In 2017, Gillette, Harry’s biggest competitor, ran an advertisement that falsely proclaimed “Most guys leave Harry’s after trying it.” So, what did Harry’s do? They reframed it as a marketing opportunity.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Check out the below ad they launched to address the elephant in the room:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="620" height="585" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare.png" alt="How Do These Razors Compare" class="wp-image-79229" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare.png 620w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-300x283.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-380x359.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-600x566.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-519x490.png 519w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-220x208.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-Do-These-Razors-Compare-385x363.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Source: <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://adespresso.com/ad/1111086/" target="_blank">AdEspresso</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>When taking action, Harry’s direct users to <a href="https://www.harrys.com/go/gdn-pro-3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">an alternative page</a>. On it,&nbsp; they address Gillette’s false advertising:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="790" height="260" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page.png" alt="Alternative Page" class="wp-image-79157" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page.png 790w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-300x99.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-768x253.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-380x125.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-600x197.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-760x250.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-106x35.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-152x50.png 152w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-740x244.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-220x72.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Alternative-Page-385x127.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px" /></figure></div>



<p>Then, they compare their razor’s to Gillette’s:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="785" height="560" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison.png" alt="Product Comparison" class="wp-image-79257" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison.png 785w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-768x548.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-380x271.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-600x428.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-760x542.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-687x490.png 687w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Comparison-385x275.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px" /></figure></div>



<p>Finally, they give users a clear call-to-action:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="483" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-1024x483.png" alt="Decide for Yourself" class="wp-image-79185" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-1024x483.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-300x142.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-768x362.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-380x179.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-600x283.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-760x359.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-106x50.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-740x349.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-220x104.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself-385x182.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Decide-for-Yourself.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h4><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></h4>



<p>During a similar campaign, they use customer testimonials to differentiate themselves from their other competitor (<a href="https://www.dollarshaveclub.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Dollar Shave Club</a>):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1010" height="723" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience.png" alt="The Shave Experience" class="wp-image-79293" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience.png 1010w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-300x215.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-768x550.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-380x272.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-600x430.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-760x544.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-685x490.png 685w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Shave-Experience-385x276.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1010px) 100vw, 1010px" /></figure></div>



<p>You won’t convert all users. That’s a given. But approaching them from different angles is an effective way to ensure you’re covering all your bases.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Items:</strong> Ask yourself, “What’s important to my customers?” Then, ask why again and again until you uncover what they really care about and what they’re really struggling with.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Finally, write ads that address the above, focusing on how your product is the vehicle that will move them from where they are to where they want to go. For more on angles, <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://charlesngo.com/angles/" target="_blank">read this article by Charles Ngo</a>.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Engage Subscribers and Increase Average Order Value (AOV) with “The CPS Method”</strong></h2>



<p>Harry’s relies on a handful of proven emails to fuel their sales engine. I identified three recurring types of email, each with a specific goal. I call Harry’s approach to email marketing “The CPS Method”:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>The three types of email focus on:<br></p>



<ol><li>Cart recovery (with a twist)</li><li>Product praise&nbsp;</li><li>Stealth promotion</li></ol>



<h3>Email #1: Cart Recovery (With a Twist)</h3>



<p>Like many e-commerce companies, Harry’s know the importance of sending recovery emails to close abandoning shoppers.<br></p>



<p>In fact, while researching for this article, I went through their checkout only to leave before buying (found out why in the bonus strategy).<br></p>



<p>A few days later, I received an abandoned cart email as expected:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="590" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure.png" alt="Choose Your Own Adventure" class="wp-image-79181" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure.png 590w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-300x259.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-380x328.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-40x35.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-567x490.png 567w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-220x190.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Own-Adventure-385x333.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px" /></figure></div>



<p>Nothing new here. That is until I scrolled down…<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="590" height="390" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan.png" alt="Not a Subscription Fan" class="wp-image-79245" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan.png 590w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan-300x198.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan-380x251.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan-53x35.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan-76x50.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan-220x145.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Not-a-Subscription-Fan-385x254.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px" /></figure></div>



<p>Harry’s offers a <em>downsell</em> to on-the-fence buyers. Why? Because they know they intrigued the user (after all, they got as far as checking out). But they also know <em>something</em> prevented them from moving forward.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Maybe it was the pricing. Or maybe, most likely, it was an objection to having to commit up-front. The downsell raises—and overcomes—their top objection and assures users there are no up-front commitments.<br></p>



<p>But there’s something else going on here&#8230;<br></p>



<p>The Truman Set is a $15 downsell. But when you go to checkout, there’s an opportunity for Harry’s to <em>upsell</em> you to a higher price point:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="613" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-1024x613.png" alt="The Perfect Addition to Your Shaving Routine" class="wp-image-79289" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-1024x613.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-768x460.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-380x227.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-600x359.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-760x455.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-740x443.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine-385x230.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Perfect-Addition-to-Your-Shaving-Routine.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>The downsell masquerades as an upsell</em>.<br></p>



<p>Expanding on this, let’s look at some rough numbers:<br></p>



<ul><li>A Shaving Plan subscription is <strong>$3</strong> on the front end with the option to upsell to <strong>$15</strong> or <strong>$21 </strong>during checking. This gives Harry’s a total of either <strong>$18</strong> or <strong>$24</strong> per customer after 30 days. (This is an oversimplification as there are many variables influencing <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-lifetime-value" target="_blank">customer lifetime value</a> such as delivery frequency, upgrading, and downgrading, etc.)</li><li>A Truman Set is a one-off payment of <strong>$15</strong> on the front end with the option to upsell for <strong>$5</strong> or <strong>$15 </strong>during checking. This gives Harry’s a total of either <strong>$20</strong> or <strong>$30</strong> per customer (with the potential to convert that customers into a monthly subscription customer down the line).</li></ul>



<p>Offering a downsell doesn’t only give Harry’s extra cash flow to offset against ad spends and customer acquisition costs (CAC). It also allows them to get a foot-in-the-door with potential subscription customers. Not everyone is ready to become a subscription customer, which, as you’ll see with Email #3, isn’t always the goal.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item:</strong> Use <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">abandoned cart</a> emails to recover revenue, of course, but go one step further. Offer a downsell to anyone who might need further coaxing to buy from you. A good downsell acts as more than a tripwire; it’s also a hidden opportunity to upsell on the front or backend.</p>
</div></div>



<h3>Email #2: Product Praise</h3>



<p>Harry’s rarely sells their products in their emails. Instead, <em>they have their customers sell for them.</em><br></p>



<p>Check out this recent email promoting their Face Wash:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="575" height="690" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level.png" alt="Get on Fred_s Level" class="wp-image-79193" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level.png 575w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-250x300.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-380x456.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-29x35.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-42x50.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-408x490.png 408w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-220x264.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-on-Fred_s-Level-385x462.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px" /></figure></div>



<p>Note the wording here. This isn’t a generic testimonial (“I love Harry’s Face Wash”); it’s a humorous confession of an advocate’s undying devotion to their favorite brand.<br></p>



<p>Building on the above, Harry’s then uses compelling copy to create a “mental movie” for what it’s like using their product:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="582" height="415" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean.png" alt="So Fresh So Clean" class="wp-image-79269" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean.png 582w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean-380x271.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/So-Fresh-So-Clean-385x275.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 582px) 100vw, 582px" /></figure></div>



<p>Using sensory adjectives and future-pacing, Harry’s walk the reader through the experience of using their product, from beginning to end, before following up with a clear call-to-action to buy.<br></p>



<p>If that isn’t good advertising, I don’t know what is.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item:</strong> Using compelling copy to get people to buy is good. But using customer testimonials who sell your products and services for you is even better.<br></p>



<p><strong>ProTip.</strong> Use humor if possible. The funnier and more memorable the customer’s quote, the more likely it is to “stick” in the reader’s mind—and convince them to buy from you.</p>
</div></div>



<h3>Email #3: Stealth Promotion&nbsp;</h3>



<p>Like many e-commerce stores, Harry’s often takes advantage of various holiday periods to engage readers—and drive more sales.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at the following email promoting around Father’s Day:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="510" height="300" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives.png" alt="Time of Their Lives" class="wp-image-79297" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives.png 510w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives-300x176.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives-380x224.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives-85x50.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives-220x129.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Time-of-Their-Lives-385x226.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px" /></figure></div>



<p>On the surface, it looks like a normal content promotion email, right? I thought so, too. That is until I clicked-through to the content and began scrolling through their content&#8230;<br></p>



<p>Halfway down the page, Harry’s invited me to buy a box set, not for myself—for my dad.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="410" height="220" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad.png" alt="Shop for Dad" class="wp-image-79265" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad.png 410w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad-300x161.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad-380x204.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad-93x50.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad-220x118.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-for-Dad-385x207.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s subtle and completely under the radar—but it works like gangbusters.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s why:<br></p>



<ol><li><strong>It “anchors” a positive emotion to their product.</strong> Anchoring describes our tendency to rely too much on the first piece of information offered (the “anchor”) when making decisions. If you’re invited to think about your father, it’s likely to influence your decision if you’re asked to buy one of their products (especially if it’s for him).</li><li><strong>Its messaging is consistent throughout.</strong> Rather than direct users to their usual store page, Harry’s created a dedicated sales page with father-focused copy to move buyers to action (pictured below). They even changed the product itself to reflect the promotion, offering a new color. Now that’s dedication.</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="443" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-1024x443.png" alt="One for The Good Guy" class="wp-image-79249" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-1024x443.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-300x130.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-768x332.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-380x164.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-600x259.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-760x329.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-116x50.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-740x320.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy-385x166.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/One-for-The-Good-Guy.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item:</strong> Content isn’t only for generating traffic, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/evergreen-lead-magnet" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">converting visitors</a>, and building links—it’s also a selling tool. Be warned, though: it’s hard to get right. Not everyone is ready to buy, remember. But if a prospect is ready, it’s a killer strategy for selling without selling.<br></p>



<p><strong>ProTip.</strong> Schedule it to coincide with a national holiday or celebration (like above) and make your offer appeal to the buyer’s family rather than the buy themselves.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e7ca290b1380" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Download Harry’s Marketing Toolkit</h2>
