										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>How to Use Psychographic Marketing to Create a Data-Driven Customer Profile</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x240.jpg" alt="Psychographic Marketing (WordPress)" class="wp-image-92432" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x240.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-768x180.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1536x360.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-2048x480.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-380x89.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-600x141.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-760x178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1440x338.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-149x35.jpg 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-213x50.jpg 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-740x173.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-385x90.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5ea1443bc32e7" class="block-preamble"><p><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">“Know thy customer.” </span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">It’s a must for all marketers regardless of your industry, niche, etc. Not only do you need to know “the who,” but you also need to know “the why.”</span></p>
</div>






<p>For your campaign to truly flourish, it’s essential to see the big picture and know what makes your customers tick.</p>



<p>That’s where psychographic marketing comes in.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f42148dc97" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
