<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Casper Marketing: How a Mattress Company Went from Zero to $750 Million in 4 Years (Case Study)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Casper Marketing [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-85998" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Marketing-Wordpress.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e871cc8a7f6a" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In 2014, five guys got together with an idea to build a company that would revolutionize sleep.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Their goal was ambitious and audacious:&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><em>To create an affordable, direct-to-consumer mattress—without the need for stuffy showrooms or sleazy salespeople.</em><br></p>



<p>Today, their company, <a href="https://casper.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Casper</a>, is valued at $750 million and serves more than 1 million customers in eight countries. (<a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/40438355/why-casper-is-the-750-million-startup-that-just-cant-rest" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Source</a>)&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>While their co-founder’ backgrounds certainly helped their initial growth, much of it has come from their innovative approach to marketing.<br></p>



<p>I recently spent a month reverse-engineering their funnel, from top to bottom. And in doing so, I found 14 killer marketing strategies you can use to get more engagement and higher conversions for your site.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In this blog post, I’ll show you:<br></p>



<ul><li>Why Casper reinvented the buying experience for their target market (and what you can learn from it)</li><li>How to create content for each stage of your funnel (even if you own an e-commerce store)</li><li>The best link building strategy I’ve ever seen (hint: it involves .edu sites)</li><li>A simple, but little-known way to “monopolize” your Google search ads</li><li>How to get customers to refer their friends to your brand (without needing to ask)</li></ul>



<p>Let’s get started.<br></p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e871d21a7f6b" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
