<h2 id="10"><strong>Strategy #10: Try This Little-Known Trick to Monopolize Your Search Ads</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re using Google search ads to grow your business, you know that you can’t have more than one search ad that sends visitors to the same site at the same time.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But that hasn’t stopped Casper from monopolizing their most profitable keywords.<br></p>



<p>Take, for instance, “casper mattress reviews,” a search query we discussed before.<br></p>



<p>Here’s what I see when I Google that term. Notice anything interesting?<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="375" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-1024x375.png" alt="Casper_s Google Search Ads" class="wp-image-86066" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-1024x375.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-768x282.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-600x220.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-760x279.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-95x35.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-136x50.png 136w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-220x81.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper dominates three out of four of the ads, directing visitors to Amazon, Google reviews, and, of course, their site. They’re all online retailers which sell their products. Further, they have a Google Shopping ad to the right making it near impossible to ignore them.<br></p>



<p>Pretty clever, huh?<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: This strategy is advanced. I’ll grant you that. But if you can pull it off, and your products are available on other sites, consider sending visitors to them beyond your own site.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="11"><strong>Strategy #11: Combine Advertising and Remarketing to Get More Leads for Your Online Store</strong></h2>



<p>You’ve probably experimented with Facebook Advertising.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And if you have, it’s likely you’ve experimented with remarketing using native advertising.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But have you ever tried both simultaneously?<br></p>



<p>Casper has. In fact, it’s something they’re doing to win new customers.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it works.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>First, Casper advertises their brand to new audiences using a Facebook Ad.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="751" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-1024x751.png" alt="Casper Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-85978" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-1024x751.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-768x563.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-380x279.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-600x440.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-760x557.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-1440x1056.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-668x490.png 668w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Facebook-Ad.png 1480w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, they entice users to click-through using a curiosity gap (“What is the social unboxing phenomenon, and why is it taking over the Internet?”).<br></p>



<p>From there, Casper sends users to <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/casper-the-warby-parker-of-mattresses/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">a CBS article</a> praising their brand’s positioning.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1024x488.png" alt="How a Mattress Company Gains an Online Following" class="wp-image-86142" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Now, you might be wondering, “What’s the point in driving traffic to a third-party site with no call-to-action, aside from building social proof?”<br></p>



<p>If you are, I pondered that, too.<br></p>



<p>That is until I scrolled to the bottom of the page…<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="503" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-1024x503.png" alt="Casper_s Native Ad" class="wp-image-86086" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-1024x503.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-768x377.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-1536x755.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-600x295.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-760x373.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-1440x707.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-740x364.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Native-Ad.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Because I had already visited their site, particularly their product page, Casper retargeted me using a <a href="https://www.criteo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Criteo</a> ad. In fact, I knew it wasn’t random because the tracking code was visible in the URL:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="28" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-1024x28.png" alt="Casper Retargeting" class="wp-image-86010" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-1024x28.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-300x8.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-768x21.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-1536x42.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-380x10.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-600x17.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-760x21.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-1440x40.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-180x5.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-250x7.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-740x20.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-220x6.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting-385x11.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Retargeting.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Mind. Blown.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: Look for a site that (a) praises your brand and (b) allows ads or sponsored links on their site. Then, experiment with driving traffic from Facebook to that site and track the number of referrals through their site’s ads.</p>
</div></div>





<h2><strong>Part 5: Email Marketing</strong></h2>



<p>Like many online retailers, Casper sends a variety of marketing emails.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here, I’ll focus on three specific email strategies they’re using to move prospects through their funnel.<br></p>



<p>Let’s move on.<br></p>





<h2 id="12"><strong>Strategy #12: Use This 2-Step Cart Abandonment Process to Recover Lost Sales</strong></h2>



<p>Casper leverage a clever 2-step cart abandonment process for recovering on-the-fence buyers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>When I abandoned my cart, I received the first of two cart recovery emails a day later.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="461" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-1024x461.png" alt="Casper_s Cart Recovery Email" class="wp-image-86038" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-1024x461.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-768x346.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-385x173.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, Casper invited me to complete my purchase. Nothing new there. But beneath the call-to-action, was a GIF, highlighting frequently asked questions, and an invite to get in touch if I had any questions.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1024x576.gif" alt="Casper_s Cart Recovery Email 2" class="wp-image-86034" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1024x576.gif 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-300x169.gif 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-768x432.gif 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1536x864.gif 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-380x214.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-600x338.gif 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-760x428.gif 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1440x810.gif 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-62x35.gif 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-89x50.gif 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-740x416.gif 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-220x124.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-385x217.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Inviting abandoning visitors to reach out isn’t just an example of great customer service, it’s also a great way to overcoming potential objections that weren’t addressed on a prospect’s first visit. Further, Casper give several ways to get in touch, making it as easy as possible for you have your questions answered and complete your order.<br></p>



<p>I chose not to return to my cart. So, a day later, I got a second email.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="788" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-788x1024.png" alt="Casper Recovery Email 2" class="wp-image-86002" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-788x1024.png 788w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-231x300.png 231w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-768x998.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-1182x1536.png 1182w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-380x494.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-600x780.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-760x988.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-377x490.png 377w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-220x286.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2-385x501.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Recovery-Email-2.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 788px) 100vw, 788px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, Casper emphasize the unbeatable guarantee we saw in Strategy #1, making it as easy as possible for me to complete my purchase.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="299" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-1024x299.png" alt="Casper Guarantee" class="wp-image-85982" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-1024x299.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-300x88.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-768x224.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-380x111.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-600x175.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-760x222.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-120x35.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-171x50.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-740x216.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-220x64.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee-385x112.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Guarantee.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>What’s most interesting about Casper, is their ability to recognize their unfair advantages—like their 100-night free trial—and use it throughout each stage of their marketing. And therein lays an important takeaway:<br></p>



<p>You might not be able to compete with your competitor when it comes to free shipping, 3-month guarantees and other expectations consumers have. But, you can take what makes your business unique, and remind prospects again and again.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: If you own an online store and send cart recovery emails, give prospective buyers an opportunity to contact you. Then, help them overcome any objections they have so they can move forward with their purchase.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="13"><strong>Strategy #13: Turn Customers into Salespeople with This Replicable Referral Engine</strong></h2>



<p>If you read my post on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Harry’s Marketing</a>, you know Harry’s got 100,000 email addresses in seven days—before they made a single sale.<br></p>



<p>Casper has built a similar referral engine into their marketing, post-purchase, inviting customers to refer friends.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it works.<br></p>



<p>After buying from Casper, you get an order confirmation email. Nothing new there. But here’s where it gets interesting…<br></p>



<p>In the email footer, there’s a referral link to refer friends and earn rewards.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="538" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-1024x538.png" alt="Casper_s Referral Program in Email Footer" class="wp-image-86106" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-1024x538.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-300x158.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-768x403.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-380x200.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-600x315.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-760x399.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-740x389.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-220x116.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Source: <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://reallygoodemails.com/wp-content/uploads/thank-you-for-your-order-r650000650.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Really Good Emails</a></em></p>





<p>This creates a <em>curiosity gap</em>. The rewards aren’t specified, so you’re enticed to click-through and learn more.<br></p>



<p>When you click “Learn More,” you’re redirected to a page on Casper’s site where you’re offered an Amazon gift card in exchange for each referral you make.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>The best part?<br></p>



<p>They make sharing super simple, depending on your preferred media.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-1024x497.png" alt="Casper Referral Code" class="wp-image-86006" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-1536x746.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Referral-Code.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>For instance, if you click “Email,” Casper trigger a prewritten email so you don’t even have to write the message yourself.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="710" height="610" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email.png" alt="Casper_s Prewritten Email" class="wp-image-86102" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email.png 710w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-300x258.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-380x326.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-600x515.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-570x490.png 570w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-220x189.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-385x331.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px" /></figure></div>



<p>It saves you time, and it’s a great way to simplify leaving a review.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: Your customers are your greatest salespeople. So, invite them to refer others—and incentivize them for doing so. You might not be able to refer Amazon Gift Cards (few can), but you can offer them <em>something</em> (e.g. a discount on a future purchase).</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="14"><strong>Strategy #14: Get Better Customer Reviews with This Simple, Yet Powerful Copy Hack</strong></h2>



<p>As mentioned above, Casper uses their order confirmation emails to invite new customers to refer friends.<br></p>



<p>But that hasn’t always been their strategy…<br></p>



<p>In the beginning, while building their authority in their marketplace, Casper built their reputation through asking for <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">reviews</a>.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it worked:<br></p>



<p>A few days after becoming a new customer, Casper would invite you to leave a review on their site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="858" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png" alt="Casper_s Review Email" class="wp-image-86110" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-300x251.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-768x643.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-380x318.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-600x503.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-760x637.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-585x490.png 585w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-220x184.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email-385x322.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>After clicking the call-to-action, you would have been redirected to Casper’s review page. On it, Casper would have invited you to leave feedback using several questions as prompts.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="749" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1024x749.png" alt="Casper_s Review Submission Form" class="wp-image-86114" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1024x749.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-300x219.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-768x562.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1536x1123.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-380x278.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-600x439.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-760x556.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1440x1053.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-670x490.png 670w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper knows consumers tend to write generic reviews when asked, so, back then, they guided customers to write about areas important to them (Casper). This included the unboxing experience and whether the customers would recommend Casper to a friend.<br></p>



<p>And it worked.<br></p>



<p>Casper has hundreds of reviews that meet all of the above.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="247" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-1024x247.png" alt="Casper Review" class="wp-image-86014" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-1024x247.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-300x72.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-768x185.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-1536x370.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-380x92.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-600x145.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-760x183.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-1440x347.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-145x35.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-207x50.png 207w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-740x178.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-385x93.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review.png 1680w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Today, Casper repurpose these reviews in the marketing, particularly in their onboarding emails. Here’s the fourth email you receive after signing up for updates from Casper:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="598" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-1024x598.png" alt="Review in Email" class="wp-image-86182" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-1024x598.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-768x449.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-380x222.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-600x351.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-760x444.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-740x432.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-220x129.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email-385x225.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Review-in-Email.png 1198w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>No amount of copy you write will ever outperform praise from a customer. So, use glaring reviews in your emails. And use them often.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: Invite new customers to review their purchase after enough time passes. Then, guide them on what to say, based on potential objections to buying your product or areas you want to highlight. Finally, repurpose those reviews throughout your marketing.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>




