<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>6 Brands That Have Nailed Their Product Marketing (and What You Can Learn From Them)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1024x240.jpg" alt="Product Marketing (WordPress)" class="wp-image-74057" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1024x240.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-768x180.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1536x360.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-2048x480.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-380x89.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-600x141.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-760x178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1440x338.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-149x35.jpg 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-213x50.jpg 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-740x173.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Product-Marketing-Wordpress-1-385x90.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e734a2b6d75a" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As a marketer, there’s probably one feeling you want to evoke in your audience more than any other:</span></p>
</div>






<p>You want your audience to get <em>excited</em> about your product so they’ll become loyal customers.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="500" height="318" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chris-Pratt.gif" alt="Chris-Pratt" class="wp-image-74021"/></figure></div>



<p>So how do you evoke this feeling?<br></p>



<p>By implementing a product marketing strategy that captures your audience and gives them a reason to purchase your product.<br></p>



<p>And that’s exactly what you’ll learn to do in this article.<br></p>



<p>I’ll show you examples of brands that have mastered product marketing and explain how you, too, can market <em>your</em> products so that you <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/onboarding-emails" target="_blank">engage your audience</a> and get more customers.<br></p>



<p>I’ll show you examples of brands that have mastered product marketing and explain how you, too, can market <em>your</em> products so that you <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/onboarding-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">engage your audience</a> and get more customers.<br></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f42148dc97" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">FREE DOWNLOADABLE BONUS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Want More Growth Marketing Strategies?</h2>
