<h1 class="has-text-align-center"> Beardbrand Marketing: How to Turn $30 into $100,000 MRR (Case Study) </h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Beardbrand Marketing (WordPress)" class="wp-image-75143" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Marketing-Wordpress.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e7496017b6d3" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When Eric Bandholz couldn’t grow a beard at his corporate bank job, he did the next best thing: </span></p>
</div>






<p><em>He quit and built a men’s grooming company.</em><br></p>



<p>Today, that company, Beardbrand, is a household name, pulling in over $100k/mo.<br></p>



<p>I recently spent a month reverse-engineering Beardbrand’s entire <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">marketing funnel</a>, from top to bottom&#8230;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And today, <strong>I want to share with you 13 strategies you can use to grow your online store</strong> … even if you don’t have a big marketing budget.<br></p>



<p>Sound good?<br></p>



<p>Let’s get to it!<br></p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e74966c7b6d4" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Download Beardbrand’s Marketing Toolkit</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>I found a LOT of amazing strategies while researching this post. But I couldn’t fit them all in the article. So, as a bonus, I’ve compiled a swipe file of Beardbrand’s best marketing materials, including two bonus strategies (#2 is brand-new), Facebook ads, email examples, and more.</p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Download All Resources Now →">Download All Resources Now →</a>
