    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Download Beardbrand’s Marketing Toolkit">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>Beardbrand Marketing: Use These 13 Tactics to Grow Your Online Store</strong></h2>



<p>Below are 13 strategies Beardbrand use to grow their reach, get loyal customers, and drive more revenue. They won’t all be relevant to you. That’s a given. So, to save time, I’ve added a table of contents so you can jump to the strategies that interest you most.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--1:-Redefine-a-Common-Misconception-About-Your-Buyer-Persona">1. Redefine a Common Misconception About Your Buyer Persona</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--2:-Open-a-Curiosity-Gap-at-Checkout-to-Turn-Prospects-into-Repeat-Customers">2. Open a Curiosity Gap at Checkout to Turn Prospects into Repeat Customers</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--3:-Create-Content-Around-Top-of-Funnel-Middle-of-Funnel,-and-Bottom-of-Funnel-Search-Queries">3. Create Content Around Top-of-Funnel Middle-of-Funnel, and Bottom-of-Funnel Search Queries</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--4:-Increase-Your-Organic-Footprint-with-YouTube-Videos">4. Increase Your Organic Footprint with YouTube Videos</a>&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--5:-Use-“The-Marketer-Magnet-Method”-(With-a-Twist)">5. Use “The Marketer Magnet Method” (With a Twist)</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--6:-Use-“Meta-Branding”-to-Build-Do-Follow-Links">6. Use “Meta-Branding” to Build Do-Follow Links</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--7:-Repurpose-Design-Assets-on-Authority-Sites">7. Repurpose Design Assets on Authority Sites</a></p>



