<p><a href="#Strategy--11:-Turn-Prospects-into-Customers-with-a-Drip-Email-Course">11. Turn Prospects into Customers with a Drip Email Course</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy--12:-Cart-Recovery-+-Facebook-Retargeting-=-More-Sales">12. Cart Recovery + Facebook Retargeting = More Sales</a></p>



<p><a href="#Strategy-13:-The-Best-Use-of-a-Lead-Magnet-I’ve-Ever-Seen">13. The Best Use of a Lead Magnet I’ve Ever Seen</a></p>



<h2><strong>Part 1. Positioning&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>“Positioning is not what you do to a product,” writes Al Ries and Jack Trout in their book, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/0071373586/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>Positioning</em></a>. “[Positioning is] how you differentiate yourself in the mind of your prospect.”<br></p>



<p>So, how is Beardbrand winning the battle for their buyers’ attention? Let’s take a look to see what they’re doing to rise above the noise in an already crowded industry&#8230;<br></p>



<h3 id="Strategy--1:-Redefine-a-Common-Misconception-About-Your-Buyer-Persona"><strong>Strategy #1: Redefine a Common Misconception About Your Buyer Persona</strong></h3>



<p>American men are NOT shaving like they used to.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>It’s true.<br></p>



<p>According to <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/razor-beards-industry-sales-designer-stubble-a8484931.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">a recent consumer report</a>, the era of beards is causing problems for razor companies, with sales falling by 5.1% over the last year, alone.<br></p>



<p>“Today, men are not judged negatively when they skip a shave, Massimiliano Menozzi, the vice president of Gillette North America, told Nathaniel Meyersohn in <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/razor-beards-industry-sales-designer-stubble-a8484931.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">a recent interview</a>. “It is not considered lazy or disrespectful.”<br></p>



<p>But it’s not always been like this.<br></p>



<p>Years ago, skipping a daily shave was considered taboo; unthinkable, even, particularly in the workplace.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Beardbrand co-founder, Eric Bandholz, knew this feeling better than anyone.<br></p>



<p>Having worked in corporate America, Bandholz, a beardsman, himself, had experienced his share of ridicule from co-workers and society, in general.<br></p>



<p>“At work, I would get mocked for having a beard,” he said in <a href="https://www.inc.com/oscar-raymundo/eric-bandholz-beardbrand-beard-grooming-products.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">an interview with Oscar Raymundo</a>. “They’d ask me things like, ‘forgot to shave?’”<br></p>



<p>Realizing the corporate lifestyle wasn’t for him, Bandholtz left, and after a series of events found his calling &#8230; <strong>to change the way society view beardsmen and to foster confidence through grooming.</strong>&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="995" height="395" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements.png" alt="Beardbrand Guiding Statements" class="wp-image-75139" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-300x119.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-768x305.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-380x151.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-600x238.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-760x302.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-88x35.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-126x50.png 126w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-740x294.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-220x87.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Guiding-Statements-385x153.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure></div>



<p>“Before Beardbrand, beardsmen were typically stereotyped as lumberjacks, bikers, or outdoorsmen,” <a href="https://www.beardbrand.com/pages/beardbrands-shark-tank-experience" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">writes Bandholz</a>. “Even though these are awesome beardsmen, I got really tired of the ZZ Top, Duck Dynasty, and Grizzly Adams references. <strong>I knew that there were guys out there who wore a beard, but didn&#8217;t fit those traditional stereotypes.</strong>” (Bold added for emphasis.)<br></p>



<p>Much like how Casper reinvented their target market’s buying experience, <em>Beardbrand redefined their buyer. </em>&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>They built <em>assurance</em> into their marketing; a reminder that it’s okay to grow a beard—even if you don’t identify with the above stereotypes. You can have it your way.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>“I wanted to unite these groups of guys and show the world that you can be stylish, professional, be a normal dude, and have a beard,” <a href="https://www.failory.com/mistakes/beardbrand" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">says Bandholz</a>. “At the time that was a very foreign concept, so I established Beardbrand as a way to unite Urban Beardsmen and give them the tools they needed to feel confident about their beards.”<br></p>



<p>It’s important to mention, here, that redefining a buyer is about more than selling products or services; it’s about selling a community, a place where your target market feel they can belong, and contribute to, even. (More on that in Bonus Strategy #2).<br></p>



<p>Granted, it’s NOT easy. But if you can help your buyers feel good about their buying decision AND feel good about themselves when doing so, they WILL remember you for it. And that’s only a good thing.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Ask yourself, “Can I reinvent my buyer?” “How can I change what it means to buy my products and services?” “Is it possible to assure my buyers that they’re not alone?”</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--2:-Open-a-Curiosity-Gap-at-Checkout-to-Turn-Prospects-into-Repeat-Customers"><strong>Strategy #2: Open a Curiosity Gap at Checkout to Turn Prospects into Repeat Customers</strong></h3>



<p>“Marketing is not a battle of products, it’s a battle of perception,” writes Al Ries and Jack Trout in <a href="https://www.amazon.com/22-Immutable-Laws-Marketing-Violate/dp/0887306667/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>The 22 Immutable Laws of Marketing</em></a>.<br></p>



<p>And it’s true.<br></p>



<p>Today, consumers google search terms like, “buy beard oil” and feel overwhelmed with choice.</p>







<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="558" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-1024x558.png" alt="Beard Oil in The SERPs" class="wp-image-75111" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-1024x558.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-300x163.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-768x418.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-380x207.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-600x327.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-760x414.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-1440x785.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-740x403.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs-385x210.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-in-The-SERPs.png 1450w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Beardbrand knows that. They understand that it’s not about being better— it’s about being first. That’s how you win the battle for the buyer’s attention.<br></p>



<p>So, how do you do that?<br></p>



<p><em>By creating defining moments, short experiences that are both memorable and meaningful. [</em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Power-Moments-Certain-Experiences-Extraordinary/dp/1501147765/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>Source</em></a><em>.]</em><br></p>



<p>One of my favorite moments while researching Beardbrand was when I went through their checkout.<br></p>



<p>Like any profitable online store, Beardbrand knows the importance of upselling.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>After all, it’s a great way to increase your customer’s average order value (AOV).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="333" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-1024x333.png" alt="Recommended Products" class="wp-image-75299" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-1024x333.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-300x98.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-768x250.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-380x124.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-600x195.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-760x247.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-108x35.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-154x50.png 154w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-740x241.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-220x72.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products-385x125.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Recommended-Products.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But what’s even better than upselling a product is upselling a <em>subscription</em>.<br></p>



<p>Why?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><em>Because turning buyers into repeat buyers is one of the best ways of building predictable and repeatable revenue.&nbsp;</em><br></p>



<p>Beardbrand knows it’s likely happy buyers will return to buy again, so they have an “auto-restock” option on all their product pages.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-1024x640.png" alt="Tree Ranger Utility Balm" class="wp-image-75323" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tree-Ranger-Utility-Balm.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Nothing new there.<br></p>



<p>That is, until, you look closer:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="905" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock.png" alt="Auto-Restock" class="wp-image-75099" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock.png 905w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-768x204.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-380x101.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-600x159.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-760x202.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-132x35.png 132w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-189x50.png 189w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-740x196.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-220x58.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Auto-Restock-385x102.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 905px) 100vw, 905px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>They offer a “small gift” to anyone that upgrades to a monthly subscription.</em><br></p>



<p>Think about that for a moment.<br></p>



<p>Beardbrand knows the importance of continuity (more on that in Bonus Strategy #2). But they also know their competitors are likely offering it, too.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>So, to differentiate themselves, they offer an unnamed gift as a way of opening a curiosity gap.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And it’s genius.<br></p>



<p>Curiosity gaps are highly-effective, especially on pricing pages. In fact, in one experiment, <a href="https://copyhackers.com/2014/04/curiosity-gap/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Joanna Wiebe lifted conversions for a pricing page by 927%</a>.<br></p>



<p>Moments are the key to victory in the battle for the buyer’s mind. Make ‘em count.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Open a curiosity gap at checkout by offering a “small gift” to turn prospects into repeat buyers.</p>



<h2><strong>Part 2. Content Marketing&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Many brands inevitably turn to content marketing as a way to get more customers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But not Beardbrand.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Unlike their competitors that built a blog on the back of an existing brand, Beardbrand created content, first, and THEN, as demand rose, began selling products.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And it all started with a overlooked Reddit post.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>On February 12th, 2012, Bandholz publicly declared his intention to build a community for what he called the “Urban Beardsman” (a term that, perhaps even Bandholz, at the time, didn’t realize would one day become a household name).&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-1024x576.png" alt="Eric Bandholz Reddit Post" class="wp-image-75255" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Reddit-Post.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>After building a community of around 300 members comprising mostly blog readers and YouTube subscribers, <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/31/fashion/taming-of-the-beard.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>The New York Times</em></a><em> </em>reached out to Bandholz for a quote on for an article about beards.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="332" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-1024x332.png" alt="Eric Bandholz Mention in The New York Times" class="wp-image-75251" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-1024x332.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-300x97.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-768x249.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-1536x498.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-380x123.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-600x194.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-760x246.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-1440x467.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-108x35.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-154x50.png 154w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-740x240.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-220x71.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times-385x125.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Eric-Bandholz-Mention-in-The-New-York-Times.png 1805w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A day before the article went live, Bandholz and his co-founders launched an online store selling another brand’s products. As Bandholz said in <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rIUZ2nbb6EA" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">an interview with Noah Kagan</a>, “We used [the <em>New York Times </em>article] to leverage the launch of our company.”<br></p>



<p>Today, that online store that Bandholz “threw up” one afternoon generates an estimated 570,000 visitors a month. [<a href="https://www.similarweb.com/website/beardbrand.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Source</a>.]<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-1024x411.png" alt="Beardbrand_s Total Visitors" class="wp-image-75195" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-1024x411.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-300x120.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-768x308.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-380x152.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-600x241.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-760x305.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-87x35.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-125x50.png 125w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-740x297.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-220x88.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors-385x154.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Total-Visitors.png 1110w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s easy to assume much of Beardbrand’s traffic comes from PR, it doesn’t: it comes from content. Beardbrand, after all, by their own admission, aren’t just in the men’s grooming business; they’re in the <em>education</em> business.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>“We were one of the first companies to make a beard oil and invest heavily into educating the market,” <a href="https://www.failory.com/mistakes/beardbrand" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">explains Bandholz</a>. “This helped us stand out and grow organically.”&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And indeed it did.<br></p>



<p>According to <a href="https://www.similarweb.com/website/beardbrand.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SimilarWeb</a>, 86.95% of all their social traffic (18.93% of their TOTAL traffic) comes from YouTube, alone. (More on that in a moment.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="554" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-1024x554.png" alt="Beardbrand_s Social Traffic" class="wp-image-75187" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-1024x554.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-300x162.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-768x415.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-380x205.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-600x324.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-760x411.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-93x50.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-740x400.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-220x119.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic-385x208.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Social-Traffic.png 1110w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Moreover, as of writing, their YouTube channel has 879,558 followers and got 7,723,036 views in the last 30 days alone. [<a href="https://socialblade.com/youtube/c/beardbrand" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Source</a>.]<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="252" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-1024x252.png" alt="Views for The Last 30 Days" class="wp-image-75327" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-1024x252.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-300x74.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-768x189.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-380x93.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-600x148.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-760x187.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-142x35.png 142w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-203x50.png 203w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-740x182.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-220x54.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days-385x95.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Views-for-The-Last-30-Days.png 1260w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, now that we know where Beardbrand gets their organic traffic from (organic and social), let’s look at how they use it to rank for commercial keywords, build do-follow links, and more.<br></p>



<h3 id="Strategy--3:-Create-Content-Around-Top-of-Funnel-Middle-of-Funnel,-and-Bottom-of-Funnel-Search-Queries"><strong>Strategy #3: Create Content Around Top-of-Funnel Middle-of-Funnel, and Bottom-of-Funnel Search Queries</strong></h3>



<p>If you invest in content marketing, it’s likely you’re familiar with content mapping.<br></p>



<p>If you’re not, content mapping involves delivering the right content to the right prospects at the right time.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Put another way, it involves targeting specific search queries depending on where a prospect is in <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">the buyer’s journey</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Beardbrand hasn’t just mastered content mapping for their brand; they’ve monetized it.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it works.<br></p>



<h4><em>i. Top-of-Funnel (ToFu)</em></h4>



<p>ToFu visitors come from informational, how-to queries.<br></p>



<p>For example, if you’re in Beardbrand’s target market, you might search for “how to grow a beard.”<br></p>



<p>And if you do, you will see Beardbrand ranking #2 for that term.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="329" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-1024x329.png" alt="How to Grow a Beard" class="wp-image-75263" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-1024x329.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-300x96.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-768x247.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-380x122.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-600x193.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-760x244.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-109x35.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-156x50.png 156w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-740x238.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-220x71.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard-385x124.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Beard.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And it’s not hard to see why.<br></p>



<p>At 7,906 words, it’s an outstanding article.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-1024x576.png" alt="How to Grow a Thick Beard Fast" class="wp-image-75267" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Grow-a-Thick-Beard-Fast.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But it also ranks for 3,329 keywords, meaning it ranks for similar keywords like “how to grow facial hair” and “what makes a beard grow.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="352" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-1024x352.png" alt="Beardbrand_s ToFu Keywords" class="wp-image-75191" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-1024x352.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-768x264.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-380x130.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-600x206.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-760x261.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-146x50.png 146w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-740x254.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords-385x132.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-ToFu-Keywords.png 1340w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While their goal isn’t likely to convert these visitors into customers, a percentage will (1) make a purchase on a whim, (2) enter Beardbrand’s Facebook and Google/YouTube retargeting flow or, (3) join Beardbrand’s email list and buy later. (More on that in Part 5.)<br></p>



<h4><em>ii. Middle-of-Funnel (MoFu)</em></h4>



<p>If you’ve ever included the word “coupon” or “discount” or something similar in a search query, it’s likely you were in the middle of a company’s funnel.<br></p>



<p>Let’s return to our earlier example. If, after reading Beardbrand’s article, you learned that maintaining a beard involves using oil or balm, you might search for something like “best beard oil and balm.”<br></p>



<p>And if you do, you’ll likely see a post explaining the difference between the beard oils and balms.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-1024x576.png" alt="The Difference Between Beard Oil and Beard Balm" class="wp-image-75315" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Difference-Between-Beard-Oil-and-Beard-Balm.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Within that article, are small calls-to-action (CTAs) to buy Beardbrand’s products.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="560" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-1024x560.png" alt="Beard Oil" class="wp-image-75115" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-1024x560.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-300x164.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-768x420.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-1536x840.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-380x208.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-600x328.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-760x416.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-1440x788.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-91x50.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-740x405.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil-385x211.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beard-Oil.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Much like ToFu visitors, not everyone will buy, of course. But that’s not the goal—Beardbrand is creating omnipotence in the men’s grooming space. And they’re hard to ignore.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h4><em>iii. Bottom-of-Funnel (BoFu)</em></h4>



<p>So, you’ve decided:&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>You need to buy beard oil or balm for your new beard.<br></p>



<p>But which is better?<br></p>



<p>You search for, “buy beard oil online” and who do you see?<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="651" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-1024x651.png" alt="Buy Beard Oil Online" class="wp-image-75235" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-1024x651.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-300x191.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-768x488.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-380x242.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-600x382.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-760x483.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-740x471.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-220x140.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online-385x245.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Beard-Oil-Online.png 1415w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>The brand that has educated you at each stage of your learning.</em>&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Aside from “buy beard oil online,” Beardbrand also ranks for several other commercial intent keywords like “beard oil buy online” and “where to buy beard balm.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="489" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-1024x489.png" alt="Buy Keywords" class="wp-image-75239" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-1024x489.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-768x367.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-600x287.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-760x363.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Buy-Keywords.png 1340w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Best of all, because they rank organically, they don’t have to invest in Google Ads, meaning higher earnings for each sale.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> If you’re investing in content marketing, create content that answers your buyer personas’ search queries at each stage of your funnel.&nbsp;</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--4:-Increase-Your-Organic-Footprint-with-YouTube-Videos"><strong>Strategy #4: Increase Your Organic Footprint with YouTube Videos</strong></h3>



<p>As mentioned above, Beardbrand’s primary marketing channel is video.<br></p>



<p>Specifically, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">YouTube</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-1024x576.png" alt="Beardbrand_s YouTube Channel" class="wp-image-75207" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Channel.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Beardbrand are prolific publishers, too. Posting on average one video a day.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="478" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-1024x478.png" alt="Beardbrand Post Daily Videos" class="wp-image-75159" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-1024x478.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-1536x717.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-600x280.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-760x355.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-1440x672.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-220x103.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos-385x180.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Post-Daily-Videos.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Of course, you could write an entire article alone on how Beardbrand uses YouTube to grow their audience. So, let’s take a closer look at two specific strategies they’re using to grow their audience.<br></p>



<h4><em>i. Focus on “How-To” Content</em></h4>



<p>If you read the previous strategy, you know that Beardbrand maps content for each stage of their funnel.<br></p>



<p>And video is no exception.<br></p>



<p>Much of Beardbrand’s videos focus on answering questions prospects have about growing and maintaining a beard.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="252" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1024x252.png" alt="Beardbrand_s How-To Videos" class="wp-image-75183" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1024x252.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-300x74.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-768x189.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1536x378.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-380x94.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-600x148.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-760x187.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1440x355.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-142x35.png 142w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-203x50.png 203w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-740x182.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-220x54.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-385x95.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos.png 1990w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But there’s another reason why they do this. And it’s easy to overlook&#8230;<br></p>



<p><em>Beardbrand embeds their videos in their content.</em><br></p>



<p>Adding video to content is a great way to boost dwell time—and that’s only a good thing for ranking higher in the search engine results pages (SERPs.)<br></p>



<p>You can see this in action, below, in one of their more popular posts: <a href="https://www.beardbrand.com/blogs/urbanbeardsman/how-maintain-beard" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">“Beard Grooming Tips: How to Maintain an Awesome-Looking Beard</a>”:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="508" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-1024x508.png" alt="How to Brush Your Beard" class="wp-image-75259" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-1024x508.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-768x381.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-1536x762.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-600x298.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-760x377.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-1440x715.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-740x367.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard-385x191.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-to-Brush-Your-Beard.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>(Note: there’s something else going on here, but we’ll come to that in the next strategy.)<br></p>



<p>Best of all, because Beardbrand creates content on their site AND on YouTube, they’re able to dominate the SERPs for certain keywords.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For instance, they rank one blog post and TWO videos for the keyword, “how to maintain a beard.”&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-1024x491.png" alt="Beardbrand_s YouTube Videos in The SERPs" class="wp-image-75211" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-YouTube-Videos-in-The-SERPs.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Not a bad way to get more traffic, huh?<br></p>



<h4><em>ii. Track All Referral Traffic</em></h4>



<p>Beardbrand is meticulous with tracking how they drive traffic to their site.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In fact, each video has a shortened URL in the video description which links to a relevant product mentioned in the video.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="209" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-1024x209.png" alt="Shop Beardbrand" class="wp-image-75307" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-1024x209.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-300x61.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-768x157.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-1536x314.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-380x78.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-600x122.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-760x155.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-1440x294.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-171x35.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-245x50.png 245w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-740x151.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-220x45.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-385x79.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand.png 1690w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you click on one of their links, you can see their tracking down to the video the user came from.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="122" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-1024x122.png" alt="Beardbrand_s Tracking" class="wp-image-75199" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-1024x122.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-300x36.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-768x91.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-1536x183.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-380x45.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-600x71.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-760x90.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-1440x171.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-180x21.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-250x30.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-740x88.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-220x26.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking-385x46.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Tracking.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Tracking referral traffic is an effective strategy because it informs you of whether it’s worth promoting on other channels like paid. Plus, you get data on which videos drives revenue—giving you more insight into what content to create in future. (More on that in Strategy 8: Promote Popular Content with Facebook Ads.)<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Create video content for your best-selling products. Then, repurpose those videos on your site where relevant. Lastly, track all referral traffic—and then double down on what works.</p>



