<h2><strong>Part 3. Link Building&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>As of writing, Beardbrand has 51,919 backlinks from 1,440 referring domains.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="790" height="110" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview.png" alt="Ahrefs Overview" class="wp-image-75091" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview.png 790w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-300x42.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-768x107.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-380x53.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-600x84.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-760x106.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-180x25.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-250x35.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-740x103.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-220x31.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Overview-385x54.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px" /></figure></div>



<p>Granted, many come from PR. But we’re not going to focus on that; you know I only want to show you what you can replicate.<br></p>



<p>So, here are three unconventional ways Beardbrand builds links and how you can, too.<br></p>



<h3 id="Strategy--5:-Use-“The-Marketer-Magnet-Method”-(With-a-Twist)"><strong>Strategy #5: Use “The Marketer Magnet Method” (With a Twist)</strong></h3>



<p>If you’ve read our post on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Harry’s marketing</a>, you know one of my favorite link building strategies is what I call, “The Marketer Magnet Method.”<br></p>



<p>Simply put, it involves doing marketing that’s so unique, other marketing blogs can’t help but write about you.<br></p>



<p>Often, it’s a link to a post, referencing a strategy you’re using. Or, in other cases, it’s a screenshot within the post itself. Here’s a nice DR:90 do-follow link we got from <a href="https://neilpatel.com/blog/influencer-market-hacks/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Neil Patel</a> recently, linking to an image from <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">this post</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="417" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-1024x417.png" alt="Neil Patel Link to Sleeknote" class="wp-image-75287" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-1024x417.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-300x122.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-768x312.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-380x155.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-600x244.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-760x309.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-86x35.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-123x50.png 123w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-740x301.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-220x90.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote-385x157.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Neil-Patel-Link-to-Sleeknote.png 1401w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But there’s another level, one that I didn’t explain in that post.<br></p>



<p><em>Doing marketing that’s so unique another sites writes an entire post about it.</em><br></p>



<p>(Yes, kind of like what I’m doing now. Pretty meta, huh?)&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>If you’ve ever visited Bearbrand’s site, you might have noticed the quiz <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/above-the-fold-examples">above the fold</a>. (More on that in Bonus Strategy #1.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="512" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-1024x512.png" alt="Beardbrand_s Homepage" class="wp-image-75179" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-1024x512.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-300x150.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-768x384.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-1536x768.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-380x190.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-600x300.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-760x380.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-1440x720.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-740x370.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-220x110.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage-385x193.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Homepage.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s a great lead generation strategy in and of itself. And with 150,000+ email addresses so far, it works. [<a href="https://www.typeform.com/blog/inspiration/beardbrand-personality-quiz/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Source</a>.]<br></p>



<p>But surveying visitors goes beyond <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">good list building strategies</a>.<br></p>



<p>Having used <a href="https://www.typeform.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Typeform</a> for the survey, the Barcelona-based startup interviewed Bandholz for an article breaking down their entire strategy.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-1024x640.png" alt="Beardbrand_s Typeform Post" class="wp-image-75203" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-Typeform-Post.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The best part? They got a nice DR:91 do-follow link back to their site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="353" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-1024x353.png" alt="Beardbrand Typeform Backlink" class="wp-image-75175" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-1024x353.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-768x265.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-1536x529.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-380x131.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-600x207.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-760x262.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-1440x496.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-145x50.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-740x255.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink-385x133.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Typeform-Backlink.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Good marketing attracts marketers. And links. But good marketing that’s done on the back of another brand’s product or service is even better.<br><br>Brainstorm the products or services you use to market your brand. Then, reach out, offering a testimonial. Or, even better, pitch a blog post outlining how you use their product or service, and how others can, too. (Nat Eliason recently did this well in <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/lead-qualification" target="_blank">this post</a>.)</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--6:-Use-“Meta-Branding”-to-Build-Do-Follow-Links"><strong>Strategy #6: Use “Meta-Branding” to Build Do-Follow Links</strong></h3>



<p>In the above strategy, we looked at how doing good marketing attracts links.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And it makes sense.<br></p>



<p>Your brand does something interesting and another site links to you for doing so.<br></p>



<p><em>But what about when YOU do something interesting. (Yes, YOU! The founder, employee, individual).</em><br></p>



<p>One thing Beardbrand is amazing at is building their company around interesting individuals with existing personal brands.<br></p>



<p>I call this “meta-branding.” You’re not just building buzz through what your company’s doing; you’re getting attention through what YOU are doing as well, on an individual level.<br></p>



<p>But meta-branding goes beyond giving a quote or an interview. It also includes giving others a reason to share your story, like <a href="https://www.shopify.com/guides/what-to-sell/online-product-opportunities" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Shopify</a> does in the below article:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="300" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-1024x300.png" alt="Beardbrand Mentioned in Shopify" class="wp-image-75147" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-1024x300.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-300x88.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-768x225.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-1536x449.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-380x111.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-600x176.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-760x222.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-1440x421.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-120x35.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-171x50.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-740x216.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-220x64.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify-385x113.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Mentioned-in-Shopify.png 1880w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As co-founder and spokesperson, Bandholz is front and center for much of Beardbrand’s media spotlight.<br></p>



<p>But it’s not just Bandholz that’s the source of good links.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For instance, in one article, <a href="https://creativemornings.com/blog-posts/5184" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Creative Mornings</a> interviewed Beardbrand’s content strategist Marque Blackman on his morning routine.&nbsp;</p>







<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="483" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-1024x483.png" alt="Marque Blackman on Creative Mornings" class="wp-image-75275" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-1024x483.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-300x141.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-768x362.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-1536x724.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-380x179.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-600x283.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-760x358.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-1440x679.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-106x50.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-740x349.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Marque-Blackman-on-Creative-Mornings-220x104.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.