<p>And <a href="https://www.wolverine.com/US/en/blog?url=%2F/wolverine_us/urban-beardsman-jeremy-lahman-introduces-the-1000-mile-waxy-brown-rough-outs/&amp;sma=sm.0000b3yrlau9cdd1xtm15dyui81lf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Wolverine</a> featured a guest post from Beardbrand writer Jeremy Lahman:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="567" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-1024x567.png" alt="Jeremy Lahman_s Guest Post" class="wp-image-75271" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-1024x567.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-1536x850.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-760x421.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-1440x797.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-740x410.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Jeremy-Lahman_s-Guest-Post.png 1825w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s unrelated to link building, it’s also worth noting that Beardbrand employees are building their personal brands on YouTube, too.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="601" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-1024x601.png" alt="Beardbrand and Friends" class="wp-image-75131" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-1024x601.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-300x176.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-768x451.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-1536x901.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-380x223.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-600x352.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-760x446.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-1440x845.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-85x50.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-740x434.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-220x129.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends-385x226.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-and-Friends.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As their employees’ reach grows, so, too, does Beardbrand’s. Win. Win.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Hire people that aren’t only good at what they do, but are sought out for their expertise. It reflects well on your brand, and it’s a great way to build links.</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--7:-Repurpose-Design-Assets-on-Authority-Sites"><strong>Strategy #7: Repurpose Design Assets on Authority Sites</strong></h3>



<p>If you’re investing in content marketing, it’s likely you’re familiar with content repurposing.<br></p>



<p>If you’re not, it involves taking a content asset, like a blog post, and using it elsewhere.<br></p>



<p>But it’s not limited to content.<br></p>



<p>Take product photography, for instance.<br></p>



<p>You invest in professional looking photos for your products, and ads to promote them. So, why not reuse them to build links?<br></p>



<p>This is exactly what Beardbrand does, though it’s so subtle it’s easy to miss.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a great example.<br></p>



<p>A few years ago, Beardbrand collaborated with award-winning designer Tobias van Schneider to create a limited-edition product called <a href="https://www.beardbrand.com/products/black-marble-beard-oil" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Black Marble</a>. (Now unavailable.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="616" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-1024x616.png" alt="Black Marble Beard Oil" class="wp-image-75219" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-1024x616.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-300x181.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-768x462.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-1536x924.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-380x229.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-600x361.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-760x457.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-1440x867.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-740x445.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil-385x232.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-Beard-Oil.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Van Schneider is building a brand of his own, so it’s no surprise that he shared the project on online portfolio site, <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/32203835/Black-Marble-Beardoil" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Behance</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-1024x640.png" alt="Black Marble on Behance" class="wp-image-75223" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-on-Behance.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But here’s where it gets interesting…<br></p>



<p>There’s nowhere to add links when you add a design, even though Behance’s links are do-follow. But there’s one place you can add it.<br></p>



<p><em>Within the image itself.</em><br></p>



<p>When you look further at Van Schneider’s submission, you can see an embedded link back to Beardbrand’s home page.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="482" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-1024x482.png" alt="You Can Purchase This Limited Edition" class="wp-image-75331" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-1024x482.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-300x141.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-768x362.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-1536x723.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-380x179.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-600x282.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-760x358.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-1440x678.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-106x50.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-740x348.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-220x104.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition-385x181.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can-Purchase-This-Limited-Edition.png 1795w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Not a bad way to get a link from a site with a DR:93 rating, huh?<br></p>



<p>Best of all, if other sites share that image or even link to that page, Beardbrand benefits from it. In fact, here’s a nice second-tier link from Abduzeedo (DR: 78)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-1024x576.png" alt="Black Marble" class="wp-image-75227" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Black-Marble.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Genius.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Add a link to your homepage within relevant design assets. Then, repurpose those design assets by submitting them to online portfolio sites.</p>



<h2><strong>Part 4. Paid Acquisition&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Content marketing works.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And for Beardbrand, it works VERY well. We know that much.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what about paid advertising?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>While it’s impossible to know how much Beardbrand invests in ads, we can get a general overview of the keywords they’re bidding on by diving into <a href="https://ahrefs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Ahrefs</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="483" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-1024x483.png" alt="Beardbrand Paid Ads" class="wp-image-75155" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-1024x483.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-300x142.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-768x363.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-380x179.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-600x283.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-760x359.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-106x50.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-740x349.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-220x104.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads-385x182.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Paid-Ads.png 1345w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Facebook, meanwhile, is a platform they ARE active on. And they are nailing it.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how&#8230;<br></p>



<h3 id="Strategy--8:-Promote-Popular-Content-with-Facebook-Ads"><strong>Strategy #8: Promote Popular Content with Facebook Ads</strong></h3>



<p>If you read Part 2, you know that Beardbrand is killing it with their content marketing strategy.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>They’re getting a TON of organic traffic. And, they’re converting a percentage of that traffic into customers.<br></p>



<p>So, it’s no surprise that Beardbrand are driving traffic to their most popular content using Facebook ads.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s a recent example promoting “Jeff&#8217;s Top 5 Beard Secrets.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="838" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-838x1024.png" alt="My Top 5 Beard Secrets Ad" class="wp-image-75279" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-838x1024.png 838w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-245x300.png 245w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-768x939.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-380x465.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-600x734.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-760x929.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-29x35.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-41x50.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-401x490.png 401w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-220x269.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad-385x471.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-Ad.png 988w" sizes="(max-width: 838px) 100vw, 838px" /></figure></div>



<p>Let’s break down what they’re doing:<br></p>



<h4><em>i. Preview content to drive more clicks.&nbsp;</em></h4>



<p>The above video is a 23-second preview of a 5:33 minute and reveals only one of the five secrets promised in the headline.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>If users are curious, they’re more likely to click through to YouTube to watch the video in full.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-1024x640.png" alt="My Top 5 Beard Secrets" class="wp-image-75283" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/My-Top-5-Beard-Secrets.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Then, if they’re ready to buy, they can click a link in the video description and buy from Beardbrand’s site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="173" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-1024x173.png" alt="Shop Beardbrand Supplies" class="wp-image-75303" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-1024x173.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-300x51.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-768x130.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-1536x259.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-380x64.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-600x101.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-760x128.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-1440x243.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-180x30.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-250x42.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-740x125.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-220x37.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies-385x65.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Beardbrand-Supplies.png 1690w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h4><em>ii. Using different calls-to-action for different users.&nbsp;</em></h4>



<p>No two users are alike.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Some are at the <em>decision</em> stage of the buyer’s journey; they already like, know, and trust Beardbrand and are willing to buy again if reminded. They don’t need to click through to YouTube and watch a video; they just need to click through to Beardbrand’s site and make a repeat purchase.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Others are at the <em>awareness</em> stage. They’re new to Beardbrand; they need to familiarize themselves with their brand before they buy from them. So, they click through to their YouTube channel to learn more.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Granted, you don’t have to use video. But it’s a great way to open a curiosity gap and drive more users to your content.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Use Facebook ads to drive traffic to your most popular content. Then, remarket to anyone that didn’t place an order, or join your newsletter.</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--9:-Answer-Frequently-Asked-Questions-to-Overcome-Objections"><strong>Strategy #9: Answer Frequently Asked Questions to Overcome Objections</strong></h3>



<p>One of Beardbrand’s most popular MoFu keywords is “styling balm vs utility balm.”<br></p>



<p>And for obvious reasons, Beardbrand has a LOT of content around answering that question.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="732" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-1024x732.png" alt="Beardbalm vs Utility Balm" class="wp-image-75119" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-1024x732.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-768x549.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-1536x1097.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-380x271.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-600x429.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-760x543.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-1440x1029.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-686x490.png 686w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm-385x275.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbalm-vs-Utility-Balm.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s no surprise, then, that they also answer that question in their Facebook ads.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="1003" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-1024x1003.png" alt="A Beardbrand Ad Comparing Styling Balm and Utility Balm" class="wp-image-75079" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-1024x1003.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-300x294.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-768x753.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-380x372.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-600x588.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-760x745.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-36x35.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-51x50.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-500x490.png 500w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-220x216.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-385x377.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm.png 1245w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Answering frequently asked questions is a great way to overcome buyer objections. Beardbrand knows decision making can paralyze prospects; given a difficult choice, they’re unlikely to buy.<br></p>



<p>So, they take two of their bestselling items, and compare them, side-by-side, to help prospects decide which, if any, is right for them. And if neither is a good fit? There’s an opportunity to get their email address, providing they visit their site, of course.<br></p>



<p>But that’s not all…<br></p>



<p>As of writing, they’re also testing their ad copy and design assets to see which converts better. Here’s a variation of the above ad with longer copy and a video:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="773" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-773x1024.png" alt="A Variation of a Beardbrand Ad Comparing Styling Balm and Utility Balm" class="wp-image-75083" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-773x1024.png 773w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-227x300.png 227w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-768x1017.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-380x503.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-600x795.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-760x1006.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-26x35.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-370x490.png 370w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-220x291.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm-385x510.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Variation-of-a-Beardbrand-Ad-Comparing-Styling-Balm-and-Utility-Balm.png 999w" sizes="(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s impossible to know how well the above ads are converting, we can assume that they’re driving sales.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And it’s not hard to see why.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Answer frequently asked questions about your bestselling products using Facebook Ads. Then, continue to optimize your ads based on their performance.</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--10:-Improve-Your-Facebook-Carousel-Ads-with-This-Little-Known-Testimonial-Hack"><strong>Strategy #10: Improve Your Facebook Carousel Ads with This Little-Known Testimonial Hack</strong></h3>



<p>In case you’re unfamiliar, a carousel ad is an ad that allows you to showcase up to ten images or videos within a single ad, each with its own link.<br></p>



<p>Carousel ads are popular with online stores for an obvious reason:<br></p>



<p><em>The more choice you offer prospects, the higher the likelihood they are to buy (within reason, of course).</em><br></p>



<p>In fact, <a href="https://digiday.com/media/facebooks-carousel-ads-10-times-better-regular-ads/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">according to one report</a>, carousel ads are 10 times better at getting people to click through compared to static sponsored posts on Facebook.<br></p>



<p>Oftentimes, a brand will add the product’s name to the description like this <a href="https://www.thinkgeek.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">ThinkGeek</a> example:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="985" height="1020" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad.png" alt="ThinkGeek Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-75319" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad.png 985w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-768x795.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ThinkGeek-Facebook-Ad-385x399.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 985px) 100vw, 985px" /></figure></div>



<p>But not Beardbrand.<br></p>



<p>They add <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer testimonials</a> to the <em>headlines</em> of their products.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="495" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews.png" alt="Beardbrand Reviews" class="wp-image-75171" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews.png 495w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Reviews-385x397.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px" /></figure></div>



<p>But they don’t just add any reviews.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><em>They add reviews that overcome potential buyer objections.&nbsp;</em><br></p>



<p>For instance, in the first review, Robert addresses its smell (“What if it doesn’t smell nice?”). In the second, Bryan address it’s longevity (“Will I need to buy it often?”)<br></p>



<p>Few are doing this. And if you’re not, now’s the time to start.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item. </strong>Use customer reviews in place of product names when using Facebook carousel ads.</p>



<h2><strong>Part 5. Email Marketing&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Like many online brands, Beardbrand sends a variety of marketing emails. (In fact, while researching this post, it was hard to know which emails to focus on.)&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Below, I’ll focus on three specific email marketing strategies they’re using to increase engagement, recover abandoned carts, and convert subscribers into customers.<br></p>



<p>Here we go&#8230;<br></p>



<h3 id="Strategy--11:-Turn-Prospects-into-Customers-with-a-Drip-Email-Course"><strong>Strategy #11: Turn Prospects into Customers with a Drip Email Course</strong></h3>



<p>Beardbrand uses a drip email course as their core <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/evergreen-lead-magnet" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">lead magnet</a> on their site. You can opt in for it through the sidebar on the blog page, or in certain blog posts.</p>







<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-1024x576.png" alt="Beardbrand Optin" class="wp-image-75151" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Optin.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s 10 emails long, and each has a CTA to either (1) increase user engagement through linking to relevant content. Or, (2) turn subscribers into customers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>While I won’t cover the content of each email, I will highlight a few interesting strategies they’re using.<br></p>



<h4><em>i. Link to Recommended Products (When Relevant)</em></h4>



<p>In Email #3, Bandholz goes deep into different aspects of beard grooming.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush.png" alt="3 Reasons to Use a Boar_s Hair Brush" class="wp-image-75075" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-279x300.png 279w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-380x409.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-46x50.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-456x490.png 456w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-220x237.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/3-Reasons-to-Use-a-Boar_s-Hair-Brush-385x414.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<p>And in the footer, he links to their combs and brushes, and includes customer reviews for those products.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="430" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email.png" alt="Bandholz Mentions Beardbrand_s Combs in The Footer of One Email" class="wp-image-75107" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email-300x217.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email-380x275.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email-69x50.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email-220x159.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bandholz-Mentions-Beardbrand_s-Combs-in-The-Footer-of-One-Email-385x278.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="370" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review.png" alt="Boar_s Hair Brush and Comb Review" class="wp-image-75231" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Boar_s-Hair-Brush-and-Comb-Review-385x239.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<p>The above happens in several emails with other products and is an effective way of introducing their offer without being “salesy”.<br></p>



<h4><em>ii. Offer a Reward Upon Completion</em></h4>



<p>When you complete Beardbrand’s 10-day email course, they offer you a gift.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="565" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward.png" alt="You Have Earned Your Beard Master Reward" class="wp-image-75339" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-300x285.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-380x361.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-516x490.png 516w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-220x209.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Have-Earned-Your-Beard-Master-Reward-385x366.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<p>But there’s a catch:<br></p>



<p><em>You can only claim it if you buy something else.</em><br></p>



<p>What’s interesting is, if you abandon your cart before checking out, Beardbrand sends you a cart recovery email.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="705" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener.png" alt="Don_t Forget Your Well-Deserv" class="wp-image-75247" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-255x300.png 255w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-380x447.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-417x490.png 417w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-220x259.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Don_t-Forget-Your-Well-Deserved-Tree-Ranger-Beard-Softener-385x452.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>And it makes sense:<br></p>



<p>If you go back to their site to claim it, you’re far more likely to buy other items, too.<br></p>



<h4><em>iii. Drive Users Back to Your Site</em></h4>



<p>As mentioned before, Beardbrand has built a loyal YouTube following.<br></p>



<p>So, it would make sense to drive new subscribers to their channel, right?<br></p>



<p>Not exactly.<br></p>



<p>One thing Beardbrand does with each email is drive users back to their site. But not just to their site; to a blog post with a relevant YouTube video embedded.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-1024x640.png" alt="Avoid This 5 Major Hair Styling Mistakes" class="wp-image-75103" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Avoid-This-5-Major-Hair-Styling-Mistakes.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s subtle, but there are a few reasons why they might be doing it.<br></p>



<ul><li><strong>Increase dwell time.</strong> As mentioned before, it’s no secret that increasing dwell time helps improve rankings in the SERPs. And adding videos to content is an effective way to keep users on-site longer.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Reduce cart abandonment.</strong> See the item in my cart in the top right-hand corner? I forgot about that. That is until Beardbrand sent me back to their site and I saw it.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Improve lead scoring.</strong> If Beardbrand scores leads based on user engagement, it’s easy to remarket to users that have clicked through in several emails to watch videos.&nbsp;</li></ul>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> If you offer a lead magnet, consider using a drip email course. It’s an effective way of linking to relevant products and driving users back to your site.</p>



<h3 id="Strategy--12:-Cart-Recovery-+-Facebook-Retargeting-=-More-Sales"><strong>Strategy #12: Cart Recovery + Facebook Retargeting = More Sales</strong></h3>



<p>Like many online stores, Beardbrand uses cart recovery emails in their email marketing.<br></p>



<p>But they use them in a way I haven’t seen before.<br></p>



<p>When I abandoned my cart (sorry guys), I got the following email shortly after.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="495" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart.png" alt="Reclaim My Cart" class="wp-image-75295" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-300x250.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-380x316.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-589x490.png 589w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-220x183.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reclaim-My-Cart-385x320.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<p>(Yes, Samuel. This is serious.)<br></p>



<p>Pretty standard, right?<br></p>



<p>I thought so, too.<br></p>



<p>That is until I browsed Facebook several hours later and saw this:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="984" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-984x1024.png" alt="Beardbrand Retargeting Ad" class="wp-image-75163" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-984x1024.png 984w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-288x300.png 288w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-768x799.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-600x624.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-760x791.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-471x490.png 471w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad-385x401.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-Retargeting-Ad.png 990w" sizes="(max-width: 984px) 100vw, 984px" /></figure></div>



<p>That’s right:&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Beardbrand uses a cart recovery email AND a Facebook retargeting ad to close forgetful buyers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And best of all, they use a carousel ad, meaning they have several ways to lure users back to their site.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Create a “catalog” on Facebook to generate dynamic ads for your products and show personalized recommendations to people who view your ad.</p>



<h3 id="Strategy-13:-The-Best-Use-of-a-Lead-Magnet-I’ve-Ever-Seen"><strong>Strategy #13: The Best Use of a Lead Magnet I’ve Ever Seen</strong></h3>



<p>After a few weeks of going through Beardbrand’s email marketing funnel, I got this email:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="680" height="720" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free.png" alt="You Can_t Beat Free" class="wp-image-75335" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free.png 680w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-283x300.png 283w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-380x402.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-600x635.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-47x50.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-463x490.png 463w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-220x233.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Can_t-Beat-Free-385x408.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, I clicked through to their site to download my free poster.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="512" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-1024x512.png" alt="Posters" class="wp-image-75291" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-1024x512.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-300x150.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-768x384.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-1536x768.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-380x190.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-600x300.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-760x380.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-1440x720.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-740x370.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-220x110.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters-385x193.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Posters.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But when I clicked “Shop” to download my favorite, I noticed I had to “shop” for it, meaning I had to <em>go through their checkout</em>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-1024x576.png" alt="Add to Cart" class="wp-image-75087" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-to-Cart.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, I added it to my cart and noticed something interesting. See if you notice it&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="384" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-1024x384.png" alt="Anatomy of a Beard Poster Checkout" class="wp-image-75095" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-1024x384.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-300x113.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-768x288.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-1536x576.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-380x143.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-600x225.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-760x285.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-1440x540.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-93x35.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-133x50.png 133w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-740x278.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-220x83.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout-385x144.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Anatomy-of-a-Beard-Poster-Checkout.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>







<p>That’s right:&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><em>They recommended similar products.</em><br></p>



<p>But not just any recommended products: PAID recommended products.<br></p>



<p>In-between the free poster you’re “ordering” and another poster is a low-priced t-shirt.<br></p>



<p>In fact, they even do it once more in the confirmation email after checking out. (Yes, they send a confirmation email for a free item.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="595" height="385" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email.png" alt="You Might Also Like in Email" class="wp-image-75343" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-300x194.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-400x260.png 400w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-380x246.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-54x35.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-77x50.png 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-220x142.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Might-Also-Like-in-Email-385x249.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s smart offering paid products with free products, but it doesn’t end there.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>You have to add your shipping information.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-1024x576.png" alt="The Best Decision You_ve Made All Day" class="wp-image-75311" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Best-Decision-You_ve-Made-All-Day.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s smart, because it allows Beardbrand to:<br></p>



<ul><li><strong>Add new users to their newsletter.</strong> Rather than assume visitors came from their newsletter, Beardbrand gives users who came through a referral or another channel a chance to join their email list.</li><li><strong>Reduce cart abandonment.</strong> I know: why would Beardbrand need your shipping information to send you a digital download? I thought so, too. Until I thought about it and realized there’s a checkbox to grant them permission to save your information for next time … making it quick and easy for you to check out, if/when you become a future customer.</li><li><strong>Validate potential new markets.</strong> It’s likely a brand like Beardbrand analyze their demographic data to determine new geographic locations to market to. Having this type of information on hand makes it a LOT easier for them to do so.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ul>



<p>It’s a great strategy, and it must be working, as they’re also driving paid traffic to it.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="495" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman.png" alt="Become The Ultimate Beardsman" class="wp-image-75215" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman.png 495w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-The-Ultimate-Beardsman-385x397.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px" /></figure></div>



<p>My favorite part?<br></p>



<p>If you don’t check out, you get not one, but TWO cart recovery emails. (Yes, even for a poster.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="655" height="760" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster.png" alt="Cart Recovery Email for Poster" class="wp-image-75243" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster.png 655w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-259x300.png 259w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-380x441.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-600x696.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-422x490.png 422w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-220x255.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Recovery-Email-for-Poster-385x447.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 655px) 100vw, 655px" /></figure></div>



<p>Driving users back to their site gives them a greater chance to upsell them. Or, remarket to them later.<br></p>



<p>As the old adage goes, if it works, do more of it.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Rather than offer freebies through a link, invite users to go-through checkout to capture more information. Then, offer recommended products to turn them into customers.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


