            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Want More Growth Marketing Strategies?">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>7 E-Commerce Case Studies You Need to See</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Increase Conversions with Compelling Copy</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Build Powerful Backlinks to Your Online Store</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Create Content for Each Stage of Your Funnel</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Recover Abandoned Carts with a Twist</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Make the Most of Your Customer Reviews</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Create an Irresistible Unboxing Experience</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Turn One-Time Shoppers into Repeat Customers</a></p>





<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Increase Conversions with Compelling Copy</strong></h2>



<p>Good e-commerce brands don’t rely on attention-grabbing visuals or big advertising budgets—they go above and beyond to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">write compelling copy</a> that convinces users at every stage of their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">sales funnel</a>.<br></p>



<p>Only with well-crafted and persuasive copy, can they position themselves as the best option in the market.<br></p>



<p>To follow the path of leading brands, start with your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">value proposition</a> and answer the problems you’re solving with your products.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Then, repurpose your value proposition across different channels, such as your site, social media content, email marketing, and paid ads.<br></p>



<p>While there’s no one-size-fits-all recipe for crafting a good value proposition, there’s one proven <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/copywriting-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">copywriting</a> formula you can try: <strong>Problem, Agitation, Solution (PAS).</strong><br></p>



<p>It’s as simple as it sounds:<br></p>



<ol><li>You define a problem;</li><li>Agitate the reader’s emotions;</li><li>Offer a solution.</li></ol>



<p>Take this example by Bellroy and how they use PAS in their value proposition:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="397" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-1024x397.png" alt="Bellroy_s Value Proposition" class="wp-image-82548" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-1024x397.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-300x116.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-768x298.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-380x147.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-600x233.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-760x295.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-1440x559.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-90x35.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-129x50.png 129w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-740x287.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-220x85.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1-385x149.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1.png 1534w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Bellroy, first, introduces a common problem among their target audience: <em>getting weighed down by baggage, bulk, stuff.</em><br></p>



<p>Then, they touch upon the results caused by this problem and agitate the reader’s responses: <em>It can slow you down and narrow your view.</em><br></p>



<p>Finally, they relieve you by saying that <em>it doesn’t need to be that way.</em><br></p>



<p>Because Bellroy’s products are <em>the </em>solution to your problems.<br></p>



<p>The PAS formula is easy to replicate for your brand, once you find the answers to the following questions:<br></p>



<ol><li>What are your buyer persona’s typical problems?</li><li>How do these problems affect their lives?</li><li>How do you solve them with your products?</li></ol>



<p>With a similar approach, you can promise to free your prospects from <em>pain</em>.<br></p>



<p>See how Bellroy positions their products as a solution that’ll save you from lots of trouble in their ads:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="968" height="242" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1.png" alt="Bellroy Google Search Campaign" class="wp-image-82544" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1.png 968w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-300x75.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-768x192.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-380x95.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-600x150.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-760x190.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-140x35.png 140w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-200x50.png 200w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-740x185.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-220x55.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-1-385x96.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 968px) 100vw, 968px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you click the ad, this is what you see:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="740" height="475" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear.png" alt="Bellroy Copy Fear" class="wp-image-82540" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-300x193.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-380x244.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-600x385.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-78x50.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-220x141.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Copy-Fear-385x247.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px" /></figure></div>



<p>Bellroy makes it easy for you to relate to the problems they solve. And they promise to free you from problems, pain, and panic.<br></p>



<p>Use the PAS formula to address prospects’ fears and pain points, and offer your products as the best solution for them.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Further Reading</strong></h3>





<ul><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/bellroy-marketing">Bellroy Marketing: 7 Million-Dollar Growth Secrets of an E-Commerce Innovator (Case Study)</a></li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Build Powerful Backlinks to Your Online Store</strong></h2>



<p>Even though most online stores rely on Google search for their organic traffic today, few e-commerce marketers know and appreciate the importance of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-seo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">e-commerce SEO</a>.<br></p>



<p>And even fewer spend enough time and effort on link building.<br></p>



<p>Getting high authority sites to link to your online store will make your domain more powerful. And a powerful domain will help you outrank your competitors in search engine result pages (SERPs).<br></p>



<p>I’ll be honest—link building takes time and effort, but the results are worth it.<br></p>



<p>No matter if you’re selling men’s apparel, design furniture, children’s books, or personalized gifts—chances are, your e-commerce site specializes in something.<br></p>



<p>And there’s a greater chance that many publishers are already writing articles about the best products in your industry.<br></p>



<p>Here comes into play, what Sam calls, <em>“The Best-Of Backlink Builder”</em> strategy.<br></p>



<p>Simply put, you reach out to authority domains in your industry and ask to get featured in their “best-of” content.<br></p>



<p>MeUndies is a great example of this. You can see them on BuzzFeed under <a href="https://www.buzzfeed.com/kevinsmith/dope-shit-for-the-dope-guy-in-your-life" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">“21 Inexpensive Gifts For The Cool Guy In Your Life”</a> &#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="875" height="382" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies.png" alt="BuzzFeed MeUndies" class="wp-image-82552" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies.png 875w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-768x335.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-600x262.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-760x332.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-740x323.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BuzzFeed-MeUndies-385x168.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 875px) 100vw, 875px" /></figure></div>



<p>… as well as on smaller sites, like <a href="https://www.thepearlsource.com/blog/valentines-day-gifts-men-appreciate-love-use/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">The Pearl Source</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="631" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-1024x631.png" alt="MeUndies Featured in The Pearl Source" class="wp-image-82616" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-1024x631.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-300x185.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-768x473.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-380x234.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-600x370.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-760x468.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-740x456.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-220x136.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1-385x237.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1.png 1095w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Getting backlinks from these “best-of” articles helps MeUndies rank for several competitive keywords, such as “boxer briefs”:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="504" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-1024x504.png" alt="MeUndies SERP Results" class="wp-image-82620" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-1024x504.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-768x378.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-600x295.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-760x374.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-740x364.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-SERP-Results.png 1150w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>(Note the number of backlinks they have.)<br></p>



<p>MeUndies also sponsors several podcasts, both to get high-quality links and to expand their reach to new audiences.<br></p>



<p>That’s why they create dedicated landing pages for each podcast they sponsor and offer their listeners a special discount:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="620" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-1024x620.png" alt="MeUndies Bill Burr Landing Page" class="wp-image-82612" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-1024x620.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-300x182.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-768x465.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-380x230.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-600x363.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-760x460.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-740x448.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-220x133.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-385x233.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page.png 1160w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>I don’t suggest reaching out to the biggest names in your industry and spend all your budget on sponsorships. However, this strategy is worth testing with small, niche-specific podcasts. You can also build strong links and expand your reach by sponsoring local events or awards.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
