</div></div>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Create Content for Each Stage of Your Funnel</strong></h2>



<p>Whether you’re a novice in your field or a seasoned marketer, it’s likely you know about the effectiveness of content.<br></p>



<p>E-commerce content marketing can help you acquire new leads and convert them into customers.<br></p>



<p>But no piece of content will work the same for different people.<br></p>



<p>Users at different stages of your sales funnel have different questions, concerns, and needs. That’s why you need to align your content marketing with the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">buyer’s journey</a>.<br></p>



<p>This doesn’t mean that you need to write 5,000-word blog posts for different segments each week. It simply means that you need to find the questions in your prospects’ minds and answer them with your content.<br></p>



<p>Take Beardbrand as an example.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>The company’s ToFu prospects most likely have questions about how to grow a beard. And when they Google that term, they’ll see Beardbrand after featured snippets:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="465" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-1024x465.png" alt="Beardbrand SERPs" class="wp-image-82528" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-1024x465.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-300x136.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-768x349.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-380x173.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-600x273.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-760x345.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-77x35.png 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-110x50.png 110w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-740x336.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-220x100.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs-385x175.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-SERPs.png 1052w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Why does Beardbrand rank so well for that term? Well, beyond having a strong backlink profile, they have a highly-detailed guide about how to grow a beard:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="973" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-1024x973.png" alt="Beardbrand ToFu Content" class="wp-image-82532" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-1024x973.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-300x285.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-768x730.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-380x361.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-600x570.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-760x723.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-515x490.png 515w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-220x209.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-385x366.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-ToFu-Content.png 1054w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Once you learn that you need to take better care of your beard, you slowly become interested in Beardbrand products.<br></p>



<p>This means you then become a middle-of-funnel (MoFu) prospect for the company.<br></p>



<p>At this stage, Beardbrand has content to educate you while subtly promoting their products. So if you’re wondering what the difference is between beard oil and beard balm, you’ll most likely end up on another one of their blog posts:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="745" height="696" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content.png" alt="Beardbrand MoFu Content" class="wp-image-82524" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content.png 745w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-300x280.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-380x355.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-600x561.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-54x50.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-524x490.png 524w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-220x206.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-385x360.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /></figure></div>



<p>And in that blog post, you’ll see <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> (CTA) buttons to buy their products:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="754" height="705" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA.png" alt="Beardbrand CTA" class="wp-image-82520" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA.png 754w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-300x281.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-380x355.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-600x561.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-524x490.png 524w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-220x206.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand-CTA-385x360.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 754px) 100vw, 754px" /></figure></div>



<p>If blogging isn’t a part of your marketing strategy, try creating “how-to” videos to educate your target audience and subtly promote your products, just like Beardbrand does:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="252" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-1024x252.png" alt="Beardbrand_s How-To Videos" class="wp-image-82536" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-1024x252.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-300x74.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-768x189.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-1536x378.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-380x94.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-600x148.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-760x187.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-1440x355.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-142x35.png 142w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-203x50.png 203w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-740x182.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-220x54.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1-385x95.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Beardbrand_s-How-To-Videos-1.png 1990w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Visit Reddit or Quora to understand what your prospects are discussing, then create content to answer their questions. Implement product marketing into your content strategy, without being salesy.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
