</div></div>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Recover Abandoned Carts with a Twist</strong></h2>



<p>Cart abandonment is every e-commerce marketer’s nightmare.<br></p>



<p>According to <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Baymard</a>, the average <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">cart abandonment rate</a> for e-commerce is close to 70%. This means that most of your visitors will leave your site without buying the items in their basket.<br></p>



<p>While cart abandonment is inevitable, luckily there’s something you can do to minimize it.<br></p>



<p>With an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">optimized checkout</a> and well-written <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">abandoned cart emails</a>, you can go beyond recovering the abandoned carts—and even sell more.<br></p>



<p>In the end, you’ll not only recover potential lost revenue but also increase the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/average-order-value" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">average order value</a> (AOV).<br></p>



<p>Harry’s has a genius strategy to reclaim abandoned carts (with a twist.)<br></p>



<p>When you leave Harry’s’ site without starting your subscription, you receive an email that reminds you to complete the process.<br></p>



<p>At first, it looks like any other abandoned cart email:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="575" height="809" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email.png" alt="Harry_s Abandoned Cart Email" class="wp-image-82588" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email.png 575w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-213x300.png 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-380x535.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-36x50.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-348x490.png 348w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-220x310.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-385x542.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px" /></figure></div>



<p>In the first part of the email, Harry’s reminds you about the benefit of buying a subscription plan.<br></p>



<p>But in the second part, things get interesting.<br></p>



<p>Harry’s offers you a <em>downsell, </em>in case you’re not ready to commit to a subscription.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But they don’t stop there.<br></p>



<p>When you follow the link and add the Truman Set to your cart, this time they <em>upsell </em>with a popup suggesting a mystery item.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="477" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-1024x477.png" alt="Harry_s Upsell Popup" class="wp-image-82592" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-1024x477.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-600x279.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-760x354.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup.png 1387w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This way, they take you back to a higher price point, even if you’re not ready for committing to a subscription plan.</p>


<div id="editors-note-block_5f89960661d62" class="block-editors-note">
    <h3>Editor&#8217;s Note</h3>
    <div><p>If you want to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/upselling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">upsell</a> a customer with an exclusive mystery item (or any item for that matter), you can create a campaign with our new <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/sitedata" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Site Data condition</a> and display the popup to visitors who exceed a certain basket value.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-76284 size-full" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData.png" alt="Sleeknote SiteData" width="707" height="411" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData.png 707w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-380x221.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-600x349.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-385x224.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 707px) 100vw, 707px" /></p>
