<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Make the Most of Your Customer Reviews</strong></h2>



<p>When it comes to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer testimonials</a>, there are two main challenges waiting for e-commerce marketers:<br></p>



<ol><li>Collecting as many rich and insightful reviews as possible; and</li><li>Using those reviews in the best way possible to convince your prospects to buy from you.</li></ol>



<p><em>How</em> you’re <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/how-to-ask-for-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">asking for testimonials</a> can have a huge impact on both the quantity and the quality of the reviews you collect.<br></p>



<p>Even if you convince your customers to leave a product review, most of the times they’re too generic and broad.<br></p>



<p>Casper finds a clever solution to this common problem. A few days after you become a customer, the company sends you this email asking for a product review:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="858" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png" alt="Casper_s Review Email" class="wp-image-82572" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-300x251.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-768x643.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-380x318.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-600x503.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-760x637.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-585x490.png 585w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-220x184.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email-385x322.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper_s-Review-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you click the CTA button, you land on a page where you can submit the following form and leave a review:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="743" height="672" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form.png" alt="Casper Review Form" class="wp-image-82560" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form.png 743w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-300x271.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-380x344.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-600x543.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-55x50.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-542x490.png 542w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-220x199.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Form-385x348.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper invites you to answer some specific questions rather than leaving it completely open-ended. This way, it becomes easier for their customers to fill the form.<br></p>



<p>Plus, they get richer and more meaningful product reviews, like this:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="963" height="218" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example.png" alt="Casper Review Example" class="wp-image-82556" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example.png 963w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-300x68.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-768x174.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-380x86.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-600x136.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-760x172.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-960x218.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-155x35.png 155w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-221x50.png 221w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-740x168.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-220x50.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Review-Example-385x87.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 963px) 100vw, 963px" /></figure></div>



<p>How you display your reviews is as important as collecting them.<br></p>



<p>You can repurpose your customer testimonials across several channels: Use them in your emails, product pages, paid ads, and many more.<br></p>



<p>Take inspiration from Casper again. They both display customer reviews on a dedicated page…<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-1024x411.png" alt="Casper Reviews Page" class="wp-image-82564" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-1024x411.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-300x120.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-768x308.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-380x152.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-600x241.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-760x305.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-87x35.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-125x50.png 125w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-740x297.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-220x88.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page-385x154.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Reviews-Page.png 1413w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>… and use it in their email marketing as <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">social proof</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="735" height="804" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing.png" alt="Casper Social Proof in Email Marketing" class="wp-image-82568" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing.png 735w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-274x300.png 274w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-380x416.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-600x656.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-46x50.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-448x490.png 448w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-220x241.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Casper-Social-Proof-in-Email-Marketing-385x421.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px" /></figure></div>



