<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Create an Irresistible Unboxing Experience</strong></h2>



<p>With the rise of user-generated content and electronic word-of-mouth, the phenomenon of unboxing made a quick entrance into our lives.<br></p>



<p>It’s not a coincidence that today <a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/unboxtherapy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">a YouTube channel on unboxing</a> has over 14 million subscribers.<br></p>



<p>Both consumers and marketers <em>love</em> unboxing videos. Because they help consumers get a detailed overview of the products they’re interested in. And they mean social proof and more reach for marketers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In order to create an irresistible unboxing experience for your customers, you need to set their expectations from the start.<br></p>



<p>Man Crates does that well by teasing the unboxing experience. When you enter your zip code on one of their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product pages</a>, the company gives you an estimated delivery date:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-1024x497.png" alt="Man Crates Estimate Delivery Date" class="wp-image-82596" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date.png 1204w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Plus, they give you more information about <em>how </em>your delivery will ship:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="596" height="355" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships.png" alt="Man Crates How It Ships" class="wp-image-82604" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships.png 596w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-300x179.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-380x226.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-220x131.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-385x229.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 596px) 100vw, 596px" /></figure></div>



<p>During checkout, they also let you write a gift note and enhance the gift recipient’s unboxing experience.<br></p>



<p>And even better, they suggest some fun pre-written notes to choose from:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="238" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-1024x238.png" alt="Man Crates Gift Note" class="wp-image-82600" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-1024x238.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-300x70.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-768x178.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-380x88.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-600x139.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-760x176.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-151x35.png 151w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-216x50.png 216w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-740x172.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-220x51.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note-385x89.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Gift-Note.png 1388w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Their crates don’t only come with a fun note …<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="768" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-1024x768.jpg" alt="Man Crates Unboxing Experience Instructions" class="wp-image-82608" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-380x285.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-600x450.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-760x570.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-47x35.jpg 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-67x50.jpg 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-653x490.jpg 653w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-220x165.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2-385x289.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Man-Crates-Unboxing-Experience-Instructions-2.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>… but also with a message that encourages you to record and share your unboxing experience.<br></p>



<p>If you want even more people to take action, you can offer your customers a special discount on their next order, in return for sharing their unboxing moments.<br></p>



