<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Turn One-Time Shoppers into Repeat Customers</strong></h2>



<p>Many e-commerce marketers focus too much on getting ToFu leads and converting them into new customers. While doing that, they fail to use the full potential of their existing customers.<br></p>



<p>In fact, <a href="https://www.conversational.com/statistics-show-repeat-customers-spend-more-and-more-often/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">repeat customers spend around 67% more</a> than your new customers.<br></p>



<p>But without the right incentive, your customers will have little reason to return to your store.<br></p>



<p>With an attractive <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer loyalty program</a>, you can turn one-time purchases into repeat buyers and increase your revenue dramatically.<br></p>



<p>Knowing this well, Sunski has a unique customer loyalty program that rewards their customers for different actions they take.<br></p>



<p>Going beyond shopping points, they offer you many other ways to earn credit:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="763" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-1024x763.jpg" alt="Sunski Earn Credit" class="wp-image-82624" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-1024x763.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-300x224.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-768x572.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-380x283.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-600x447.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-760x566.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-47x35.jpg 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-67x50.jpg 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-658x490.jpg 658w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-220x164.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1-385x287.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Earn-Credit-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As part of their customer loyalty program, the company also uses <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/referral-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">referral marketing</a>.<br></p>



<p>All you need to do is to write your friend’s email address and Sunski takes care of the rest for you.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="451" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-1024x451.jpg" alt="Sunski Refer a Friend" class="wp-image-82628" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-1024x451.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-768x338.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-380x167.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-600x264.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-760x334.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-80x35.jpg 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-114x50.jpg 114w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-740x326.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-220x97.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1-385x169.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Refer-a-Friend-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Your friend receives the following email and you both get a nice $10 discount on Sunski products.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="562" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-562x1024.png" alt="Sunski Referral Email" class="wp-image-82632" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-562x1024.png 562w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-165x300.png 165w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-380x693.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-600x1094.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-19x35.png 19w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-27x50.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-269x490.png 269w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-220x401.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1-385x702.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sunski-Referral-Email-1.png 615w" sizes="(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px" /></figure></div>



<p>This way, you don’t only retain your existing customers, but also let them bring you more customers.<br></p>



<p>The best part is, you don’t need to create a loyalty program from scratch to use referrals. You can easily set up a Shopify app or use a third-party tool to start a referral program.<br></p>



