<h2><strong>MeUndies Marketing: What You Need to Know</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re a regular reader of our growth guides, you know we usually go through a brand’s entire marketing funnel, from top to bottom.<br></p>



<p>But given 47.46% of MeUndies’s traffic is direct&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="393" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-1024x393.png" alt="MeUndies Traffic Sources" class="wp-image-75630" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-1024x393.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-300x115.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-768x295.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-380x146.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-600x230.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-760x292.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-91x35.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-130x50.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-740x284.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources-385x148.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Traffic-Sources.png 1380w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>







<p>&#8230;and only 27.73 is organic&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="630" height="610" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic.png" alt="MeUndies Organic Traffic" class="wp-image-75590" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic.png 630w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-300x290.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-380x368.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-600x581.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-36x35.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-52x50.png 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-506x490.png 506w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-220x213.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Organic-Traffic-385x373.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;I decided to focus on what they’re doing to convert BRAND-AWARE visitors into buyers.<br></p>



<p>So, with that in mind, let’s get into MeUndies marketing, starting with&#8230;&nbsp;<br></p>



<h2 id="Turn-Visitors-into-Buyers-with-a-Homepage-Quiz"><strong>1. Turn Visitors into Buyers with a Homepage Quiz&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Much like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/beardbrand-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Beardbrand</a>, MeUndies use a homepage quiz to turn first-time visitors into buyers. (The emphasis, here, is on “first-time.” More on that in a moment.)&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s how it works.<br></p>



<p>When you visit MeUndies’ homepage for the first time, you’re invited to “find your first pair” of underwear:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-1024x640.png" alt="Find Your First Pair" class="wp-image-75450" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Find-Your-First-Pair.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you click the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> button, MeUndies survey you on your preferences.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-1024x640.png" alt="MeUndies Survey Question" class="wp-image-75626" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Survey-Question.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>After you choose which type of underwear you like to wear, they ask you to choose a color:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-1024x640.png" alt="Choose Your Color" class="wp-image-75442" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Choose-Your-Color.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But there are a few things going on here.<br></p>



<p>First, “Adventurous” is the default color. Meaning, it’s the first color you see after answering the above questions. But it’s also their most expensive. For comparison, an Adventurous pair is $24, but a Bold or Classic pair is $20.<br></p>



<p>Second, there’s a subtle upsell to their membership. I’ll write more about this in Strategy #2, but for now, notice the emphasis on:&nbsp;<br></p>



<ol><li>Savings. (“Join and save 33%”);</li><li>Risk-reversal. (“Skip or cancel anytime”); and</li><li>Simplicity. (Check).</li></ol>



<p>After completing the quiz, I bought a pair of undies. (You know, for research.) But when I returned to their homepage after, I noticed something interesting…<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-1024x640.png" alt="MeUndies Landing Page Above the Fold" class="wp-image-75562" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Above-the-Fold.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>They changed their hero image.</em><br></p>



<p>And it makes perfect sense.<br></p>



<p>No one, after all, wants to see a quiz they’ve already taken. The purpose was fulfilled; it’s time to invite users to take another action.<br></p>



<p>Speaking of which, there’s something else going on with MeUndies’s <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/above-the-fold-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">above-the-fold content</a>, but we’ll return to it in Strategy #4&#8230;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Use a homepage quiz to help first-time visitors find the right product for them. Then, exclude from return visitors and customers.</p>



<h2 id="Create-an-Ascension-Ladder-to-Increase-Retention"><strong>2. Create an Ascension Ladder to Increase Retention</strong></h2>



<p>There are many ways to improve customer retention.<br></p>



<p>Reward brand advocates. Personalize your emails. Use reciprocity.<br></p>



<p>But there’s one way that’s more powerful than any other…<br></p>



<p><em>Creating a hierarchy, or an ascension ladder, ideally, through membership.</em><br></p>



<p>“When you figure out how to structure your business with ‘membership concept’ and then levels, so customers can move from one level upward to the next, and then to the next, you will have constructed a way to automatically improve retention,” writes Dan Kennedy in <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Guide-Maximum-Referrals-Customer-Retention-ebook/dp/B01B11TIFY/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>No B.S. Guide to Maximum Referrals</em></a>. “As their level of commitment increases, their longevity automatically increases.”<br></p>



<p>MeUndies get the power of taking their customers and “moving ‘em up the money pyramid.” So much so, that they recently moved to a membership model to grow their business faster.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-1024x576.png" alt="MeUndies Featured in Adweek" class="wp-image-75530" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-Adweek.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But it’s not that membership that’s worth noting here, <em>it’s how they’re selling it.</em><br></p>



<p>Take their product pages, for example. On it, there are several chances to upgrade a one-time purchase to a membership:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-1024x640.png" alt="MeUndies Product Page" class="wp-image-75602" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>First, they emphasize how much you save with a membership versus a one-off purchase:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="685" height="355" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs.png" alt="MeUndies Men_s Boxer Briefs" class="wp-image-75578" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs.png 685w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-300x155.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-380x197.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-600x311.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Men_s-Boxer-Briefs-385x200.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 685px) 100vw, 685px" /></figure></div>



<p>Second, they offer “Member’s Exclusive” prints (more on that in a moment):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="685" height="425" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive.png" alt="Member Exclusive" class="wp-image-75490" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive.png 685w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-220x136.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Member-Exclusive-385x239.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 685px) 100vw, 685px" /></figure></div>



<p>Third, they remind you again of how much you save with a membership before reversing risk with an unbeatable guarantee.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="670" height="410" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag.png" alt="Add Membership to Bag" class="wp-image-75430" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag.png 670w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-300x184.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-380x233.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-600x367.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-82x50.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-220x135.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Add-Membership-to-Bag-385x236.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px" /></figure></div>



<p>Fourth, there’s a final reminder to upgrade when you reach checkout:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="291" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-1024x291.png" alt="Become a Member" class="wp-image-75434" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-1024x291.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-300x85.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-768x218.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-1536x437.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-380x108.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-600x171.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-760x216.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-1440x410.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-123x35.png 123w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-176x50.png 176w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-740x210.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-220x63.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member-385x109.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Become-a-Member.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>MeUndies’ membership exclusivity isn’t just promoted on their site. It’s also prominent in their Facebook ads&#8230;<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1010" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1.png" alt="MeUndies Facebook Ad(" class="wp-image-75522" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-296x300.png 296w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-768x780.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-380x386.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-600x609.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-760x771.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-483x490.png 483w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-220x223.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad1-385x391.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



