<p>&#8230;and in their onboarding emails:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="982" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-982x1024.png" alt="Learn More" class="wp-image-75482" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-982x1024.png 982w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-288x300.png 288w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-768x801.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-380x396.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-600x626.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-760x792.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-470x490.png 470w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More-385x401.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Learn-More.png 1055w" sizes="(max-width: 982px) 100vw, 982px" /></figure></div>



<p>With new (albeit limited) prints available each month, there are endless ways to appeal to subscribers and convert them into repeat buyers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For instance, while researching this post, MeUndies promoted their brilliantly-titled, “Zero Fox Given” print, targeting an audience segment that identify with not caring what others think.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-1024x506.png" alt="MeUndies No Fox Given" class="wp-image-75586" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-1024x506.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-768x379.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-1536x758.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-760x375.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-1440x711.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-No-Fox-Given.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Now, however, they’re promoting their Christmas print, targeting users looking for gifts for the whole family.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-1024x576.png" alt="MeUndies Gift Guide" class="wp-image-75554" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Remember, it only takes ONE angle to convert a subscriber to the membership. And with a constantly evolving collection, and ample marketing angles, it’s only a matter of time.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>According to Kennedy, there are four reasons why customers gravitate toward memberships:<br></p>



<ol><li><strong>Value propositions.</strong> Upgrading makes sense if you’re saving money. Why pay $24 dollars when you can pay $16? (Think: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperbolic_discounting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">hyperbolic discounting</a>.)</li><li><strong>Exclusive benefits and perks.</strong> MeUndies’s exclusive prints are, well, exclusive. And with a limited run each month, they’re highly sought-after.</li><li><strong>Peer influence, “being seen,” recognized, status.</strong> MeUndies are big on highlighting members of their “MeUndies Fam” on social media.</li><li><strong>The nature and behavior of the customer.</strong> There&#8217;s a percentage of people who typically buy the most expensive option. Why? Because that’s how they see themselves. Or, how they want to be seen by others. Buying underwear is no exception.</li></ol>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Consider offering a membership to increase your customer’s lifetime value. More brands are doing it now. And for good reason: it works. Don’t get left behind.</p>



<h2 id="Build-a-Replicable-Referral-Engine-(with-a-Twist)"><strong>3. Build a Replicable Referral Engine (with a Twist)</strong></h2>



<p>If you read my post on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Harry’s Marketing</a>, you know Harry’s got 100,000 email addresses in seven days through referrals.<br></p>



<p>Not bad.<br></p>



<p>But as impressive as it is, it’s nothing compared to how MeUndies are getting referrals, consistently, customer by customer.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-1024x576.png" alt="MeUndies Referral Page(1)" class="wp-image-75606" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Here’s what they’re doing, element by element.<br></p>



<h4>i. Write a Killer Headline</h4>



<p>You know the importance of writing good headlines for your homepage. So, why not have one for your referral program, too?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Rather than writing something generic like “Refer a Friend,” MeUndies emphasize the benefits of their referral program to both parties. The referral gets 20% off their first order; the affiliate gets $20 store credit. (Or, “get free undies”, given that $20 is the average cost of a pair of MeUndies’ underwear.)&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="322" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-1024x322.png" alt="Refer a Friend" class="wp-image-75646" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-1024x322.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-300x94.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-768x242.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-1536x483.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-380x120.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-600x189.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-760x239.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-1440x453.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-111x35.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-159x50.png 159w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-740x233.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-220x69.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend-385x121.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Refer-a-Friend.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h4>ii. Simplify the Referral Process</h4>



<p>MeUndies use software called <a href="https://www.friendbuy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Friendbuy</a> to simplify referring a friend.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="750" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-1024x750.png" alt="MeUndies Referral Page" class="wp-image-75610" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-1024x750.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-768x562.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-1536x1125.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-380x278.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-600x439.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-760x557.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-1440x1055.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-669x490.png 669w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Referral-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>First, they simplify the invitation by offering multiple channels including Facebook messenger and email. Plus, they offer a fun, pre-written template to increase engagement.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s what it says:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><em>Hey&#8230;you.</em><br></p>



<p><em>This is totally your friend and definitely not a pre-written MeUndies message.</em><br></p>



<p><em>I (your friend) really think you&#8217;d love MeUndies. They are 3x softer than cotton and feature super-fun prints and colors.</em><br></p>



<p><em>Use my referral to get 20% off your first order (excluding packs).</em><br></p>



<p><em>Enjoy!</em><br></p>



<p><em>-Me. Your friend.</em><br></p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>They even offer to remind your friend if they don’t reply after three days. (Note: this checkbox is marked by default.)<br></p>



<p>When the referral receives the email, the affiliate, is cleverly mentioned in the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">subject line</a>&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="900" height="80" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies.png" alt="You Need Some New Undies" class="wp-image-75666" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies.png 900w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-300x27.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-768x68.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-380x34.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-600x53.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-760x68.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-180x16.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-250x22.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-740x66.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-220x20.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You-Need-Some-New-Undies-385x34.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;and again in the body copy to explain why the recipient is receiving the email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="695" height="565" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited.png" alt="You_ve Been Invited" class="wp-image-75670" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited.png 695w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-300x244.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-380x309.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-600x488.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-43x35.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-62x50.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-603x490.png 603w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-220x179.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/You_ve-Been-Invited-385x313.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px" /></figure></div>



<p>MeUndies use <a href="https://www.friendbuy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Friendbuy</a> to power their referral emails. So, if you’re looking for a solution, it might be worth checking out.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h4>iii. Focus on the User-Experience&#8230;</h4>



<p>MeUndies know that buyers are more likely to refer friends <em>after</em> they become customers. With that in mind, they make their referral program more visible on their site to customers. Before I became a customer, their footer optin asked me to join their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email list</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="258" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-1024x258.png" alt="Join The MeUndies Fam" class="wp-image-75478" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-1024x258.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-300x76.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-768x194.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-1536x387.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-380x96.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-600x151.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-760x192.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-1440x363.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-139x35.png 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-198x50.png 198w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-740x187.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-220x55.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam-385x97.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Join-The-MeUndies-Fam.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And it makes sense, right? After all, they want to convert as many new first-time visitors into leads as possible.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But after a became a customer, their footer optin changed, inviting me to refer a friend:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="322" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-1024x322.png" alt="Get Free Undies" class="wp-image-75458" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-1024x322.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-300x94.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-768x242.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-1536x483.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-380x120.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-600x189.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-760x239.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-1440x453.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-111x35.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-159x50.png 159w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-740x233.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-220x69.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies-385x121.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Get-Free-Undies.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h4>iv. &#8230;And the Post-Purchase Experience</h4>



<p>After buying from MeUndies, you get an email inviting you to track your order.<br></p>



<p>And when you click the link, there’s also a another invitation to refer a friend, if you haven’t done already:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-1024x470.png" alt="Throw Your Friend a Bone" class="wp-image-75658" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-768x353.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-380x175.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-600x276.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-740x340.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Throw-Your-Friend-a-Bone.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Not everyone will be ready at this stage. I’ll grant you that. But it doesn’t hurt to try.<br></p>



<h4>v. Highlight MVPs</h4>



<p>MeUndies regularly highlight a “referrer of the month” on Instagram. When you visit their profile, there’s a link to “Free Undies.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="384" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-1024x384.png" alt="Free Undies" class="wp-image-75454" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-1024x384.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-300x112.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-768x288.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-1536x576.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-380x142.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-600x225.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-760x285.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-1440x540.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-93x35.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-133x50.png 133w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-740x277.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-220x82.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies-385x144.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Undies.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And when you click on it, there’s an Instagram story promoting their referral program, highlighting their current referrer of the month:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-1024x640.png" alt="MeUndies Instagram Post" class="wp-image-75558" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Instagram-Post.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Asking for referrals is key. But, as you would when qualifying leads, timing is everything.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Invite customers to refer friends using a win-win <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank">value proposition</a> and remember to make it super simple to do. Bonus if you can offer a pre-written message.</p>



<h2 id="Create-a-Go-To-Gift-Guide"><strong>4.Create a Go-To Gift Guide</strong></h2>



<p>As mentioned before, MeUndies get a TON of direct traffic. Meaning, they don’t need to invest in content marketing like other brands.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But that doesn’t mean they don’t venture into it once in a while.<br></p>



<p>Take their recent Christmas gift guide as an example.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-1024x576.png" alt="MeUndies Gift Guide(1)" class="wp-image-75550" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Gift-Guide1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Understanding that few, if any of their customers, know what to buy for their family at Christmas, MeUndies created a go-to guide for all members of the family.<br></p>



<p>For example, there are sections “for him,” “for her,” and “for us,” appealing to couples.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="547" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-1024x547.png" alt="Gifts for Him" class="wp-image-75466" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-1024x547.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-300x160.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-768x411.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-380x203.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-600x321.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-760x406.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-94x50.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-740x396.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-220x118.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him-385x206.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gifts-for-Him.png 1300w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And when you click a section, MeUndies unveil a range of product recommendations, covering several price ranges.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="454" height="685" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26.png" alt="Gifts For Him Image" class="wp-image-75675" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26.png 454w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-199x300.png 199w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-380x573.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-23x35.png 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-33x50.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-325x490.png 325w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-220x332.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image26-385x581.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px" /></figure></div>



<p>And if you can’t find something?<br></p>



<p>There’s an option to buy a gift card, instead:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="547" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-1024x547.png" alt="Give a Gift" class="wp-image-75470" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-1024x547.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-300x160.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-768x411.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-380x203.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-600x321.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-760x406.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-94x50.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-740x396.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-220x118.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift-385x206.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Give-a-Gift.png 1300w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As of writing, MeUndies are promoting it in their emails&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="740" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide.png" alt="Shop Our Gift Guide" class="wp-image-75654" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-300x233.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-380x295.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-600x466.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-64x50.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-631x490.png 631w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-220x171.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Our-Gift-Guide-385x299.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;and their Facebook ads:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="496" height="688" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad.png" alt="MeUndies Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-75526" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad.png 496w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-216x300.png 216w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-380x527.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-36x50.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-353x490.png 353w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-220x305.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Facebook-Ad-385x534.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 496px) 100vw, 496px" /></figure></div>



<p>Of course, if they were using a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/guide-your-visitors" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Guide Your Visitors </a>campaign to target return visitors, they could drive more traffic to that page and increase product sales even further.<br></p>



<p>But that’s not for me to comment on <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f609.png" alt="😉" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item:</strong> If you offer several items under one category such as apparel, create a gift guide, categorized “for him,” “for her,” etc. Perfect for the busy holidays like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Black Friday</a>, Christmas, and more.</p>



<h2 id="Leverage-The-Power-of-Podcasts"><strong>5. Leverage The Power of Podcasts</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re a regular podcast listener, it’s likely you’ve heard of MeUndies.<br></p>



<p>Why?<br></p>



<p><em>Because they’re avid podcast sponsors.</em><br></p>



<p>While it’s hard to know exactly how many, we can assume it’s a lot as they currently have as many as 26 landing pages at any one time. (More on that in a moment.):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="572" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-1024x572.png" alt="MeUndies Podcast Landing Pages in The SERPs" class="wp-image-75594" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-1024x572.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-300x168.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-768x429.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-380x212.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-600x335.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-760x425.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-740x414.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-220x123.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs-385x215.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Podcast-Landing-Pages-in-The-SERPs.png 1315w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And that’s NOT including podcasts without landing pages. (More on that in a moment, too.)<br></p>



<p>There’s a good reason for sponsoring podcasts, and it has nothing to do with getting exposure to new audiences:<br></p>



<p><strong>You get a nice do-follow link from the podcast’s website.</strong><br></p>



<p>For instance, after sponsoring <a href="https://nerdist.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Nerdist</a>, MeUndies got a link in the episode’s show notes:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="332" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-1024x332.png" alt="Link to MeUndies" class="wp-image-75486" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-1024x332.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-300x97.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-768x249.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-380x123.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-600x195.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-760x247.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-108x35.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-154x50.png 154w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-740x240.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-220x71.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies-385x125.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-MeUndies.png 1325w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But it gets better…<br></p>



<p>Depending on the podcast, it’s possible to get TWO do-follow links.<br></p>



<p>Take <a href="https://satellitesisters.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Satellite Sisters</a>, for example. They host and publish their podcast on <a href="https://www.libsyn.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Libsyn</a> (90):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="255" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-1024x255.png" alt="Satellite Sisters Link to MeUndies" class="wp-image-75650" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-1024x255.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-300x75.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-768x191.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-380x95.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-600x149.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-760x189.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-141x35.png 141w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-201x50.png 201w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-740x184.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-220x55.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies-385x96.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Satellite-Sisters-Link-to-MeUndies.png 1245w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But they also syndicate their podcast on <a href="https://www.podbean.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Podbean</a> (DR: 89):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="168" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-1024x168.png" alt="Podbean Link to MeUndies" class="wp-image-75634" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-1024x168.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-300x49.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-768x126.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-380x62.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-600x99.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-760x125.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-1440x237.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-180x30.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-250x41.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-740x122.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-220x36.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies-385x63.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Podbean-Link-to-MeUndies.png 1460w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>One podcast. Two links. #BiWinning<br></p>



<p>But there’s one more thing I want to highlight, here…<br></p>



<p>As I’ve mentioned already, MeUndies make it super simple for visitors to buy from them.<br></p>



<p>One way they do that, at least, with podcast sponsorships, is they create a dedicated landing page for shows they’re sponsoring on an on-going basis.<br></p>



<p>Take the below page as an example.<br></p>



<p>MeUndies have a dedicated landing page for visitors coming exclusively from <a href="http://podcasts.joerogan.net/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">The Joe Rogan Experience</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-1024x491.png" alt="Joe Rogan X MeUndies" class="wp-image-75474" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Joe-Rogan-X-MeUndies.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The above-the-fold copy addresses them specifically and emphasizes their irresistible offer and their unbeatable guarantee:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="276" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-1024x276.png" alt="MeUndies Landing Page Copy" class="wp-image-75566" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-1024x276.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-300x81.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-768x207.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-1536x413.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-380x102.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-600x161.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-760x205.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-1440x388.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-130x35.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-186x50.png 186w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-740x199.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-220x59.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy-385x104.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Landing-Page-Copy.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But here’s where it gets interesting&#8230;<br></p>



<p>Rather than give visitors a discount code, they <em>auto-apply</em> it to the user’s checkout, removing a potential barrier to buying.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="640" height="799" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied.png" alt="Promotion Applied" class="wp-image-75642" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied.png 640w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-240x300.png 240w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-380x474.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-600x749.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-392x490.png 392w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-220x275.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-385x481.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></figure></div>



<p>Abandoning checkout in pursuit of a coupon code is a problem for e-tailers. MeUndies know that, so they bypass it entirely.<br></p>



<p>For the remainder of your visit, MeUndies remind you of your discount, ever-nudging you to make a purchase.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="900" height="300" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2.png" alt="Promotion Applied 2" class="wp-image-75638" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2.png 900w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-300x100.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-768x256.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-380x127.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-600x200.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-760x253.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-105x35.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-150x50.png 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-740x247.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-220x73.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Promotion-Applied-2-385x128.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></figure></div>



<p>Bottom line?<br></p>



<p>Sponsoring podcasts is a great way to build links. But sponsoring <em>syndicated</em> podcasts is even better. Choose your sponsors wisely.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item. </strong>Sponsor podcasts with audiences similar to yours. Then, creating a dedicated landing page to welcome listeners. Finally, offer a discount and, if possible, auto-apply it to their cart.</p>



<h2 id="Use-The-Best-Of-Backlink-Builder"><strong>6. Use The Best-Of Backlink Builder</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re a regular reader of our growth guides, you know one of my favorite link building strategies is what I call, “The Best-Of Backlink Builder.”<br></p>



<p>If you need a refresher, <em>The Best-Of Backlink Builder involves reaching out to authority domains in your industry and getting featured in best-of content.</em><br></p>



<p>For example, if you sell women’s yoga pants, you might search for “best yoga pants for women 2018” and try to get featured in one of the top search results:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="674" height="420" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women.png" alt="Best Yoga Pants for Women" class="wp-image-75438" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women.png 674w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-600x374.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Best-Yoga-Pants-for-Women-385x240.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 674px) 100vw, 674px" /></figure></div>



<p>Yes, it requires work. But over time, you become omnipresent &#8230; and it becomes a LOT easier to build links.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Just ask MeUndies.<br></p>



<p>One of their best backlinks, in terms of domain rating, comes from The Huffington Post in their article, “<a href="https://www.huffpost.com/entry/mens-clothing-subscription-boxes-every-guy-should-try_n_5ad8a095e4b029ebe021a5a7" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">10 Men&#8217;s Clothing Subscription Boxes Every Guy Should Try</a>.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-1024x640.png" alt="MeUndies Featured in The Huffington Post" class="wp-image-75538" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Huffington-Post-220x137.png 220w,