<p>But it’s not just for authority sites.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a recent link from a smaller site, <a href="https://www.thepearlsource.com/blog/valentines-day-gifts-men-appreciate-love-use/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">The Pearl Source</a> (DR:57):<br></p>



