></div>



<p>Best of all, by scaling this strategy, MeUndies are now ranking for some highly-competitive commercial keywords.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Take, “boxer briefs” as an example.<br></p>



<p>As of writing, MeUndies rank #2—above Amazon:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="950" height="400" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs.png" alt="MeUndies Product Page in The SERPs" class="wp-image-75598" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs.png 950w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-300x126.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-768x323.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-380x160.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-600x253.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-760x320.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-119x50.png 119w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-740x312.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Product-Page-in-The-SERPs-385x162.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 950px) 100vw, 950px" /></figure></div>



