            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Want More Growth Marketing Strategies?">    </div>
</div>


<h3><strong>Site Structure</strong></h3>



<p>Let’s start from the top.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Site structure plays an integral role in the user experience as well as where you rank in search engine results pages (SERPs).&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>So you want to get it right.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>One mistake many e-commerce stores make is getting “too cute” with their site structure to the point that it becomes needlessly complex.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>What you want to do is make sure that it’s simple and easy to navigate.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Ideally, every single product page will be a max of three clicks away from your homepage.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>After all, the more clicks a visitor has to make, the lower your conversion rate will be.<br></p>



<p>Here’s an example of an e-commerce store with a great site structure: <a href="https://soaptopia.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Soaptopia</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="436" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-1024x436.png" alt="Soaptopia" class="wp-image-73816" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-1024x436.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-300x128.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-768x327.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-380x162.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-600x255.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-760x324.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-960x410.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-740x315.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1-385x164.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-1.png 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Notice how they break their products down into categories so visitors can quickly find what they’re looking for.<br></p>



<p>Click on “Citrus” and you’re instantly taken to a relevant page for citrus soaps.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="438" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-1024x438.png" alt="Soaptopia 2" class="wp-image-73800" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-1024x438.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-300x128.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-768x329.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-380x163.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-600x257.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-760x325.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-960x410.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-740x317.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1-385x165.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-2-1.png 1357w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="440" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-1024x440.png" alt="Soaptopia 3" class="wp-image-73804" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-1024x440.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-300x129.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-768x330.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-380x163.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-600x258.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-760x327.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-116x50.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-740x318.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1-385x165.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-3-1.png 1336w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Click on a particular product, and it instantly pops up and offers you the option to add it to your cart.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="347" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-1024x347.png" alt="Soaptopia 4" class="wp-image-73808" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-1024x347.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-300x102.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-768x260.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-380x129.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-600x203.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-760x258.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-103x35.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-148x50.png 148w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-740x251.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-220x75.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1-385x130.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-4-1.png 1204w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="375" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-1024x375.png" alt="Soaptopia 5" class="wp-image-73812" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-1024x375.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-768x281.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-600x220.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-760x278.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-96x35.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-137x50.png 137w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-220x81.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Soaptopia-5-1.png 1254w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The whole process is super simple and allows you to find what you’re looking for without any fuss.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>On top of this, Google can easily index all of the site’s product pages.<br></p>



<p>So by keeping your site structure simple and well organized, you’re appeasing both customers and search engines.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Keep this in mind when designing your layout and navigation.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h3><strong>Keyword Research</strong></h3>



<p>Performing keyword research is a critical step that will impact the rest of the process from here on out.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>There are a few ways to go about this. You could always use the Google Keyword Planner, which can yield some decent results.<br></p>



<p>But I like to think outside the box and gain a better understanding of what online shoppers are really looking for.<br></p>



<p>One technique that can do wonders is simply using <a href="https://www.amazon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Amazon</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Of course, Amazon is likely one of your main competitors considering that they <a href="https://www.recode.net/2017/10/24/16534100/amazon-market-share-ebay-walmart-apple-ecommerce-sales-2017" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">accounted for nearly half</a> of all e-commerce sales in 2017.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what better way to get a pulse on what online shoppers are looking for than using Amazon Suggest?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And it’s really quite easy. Here’s an example:<br></p>



<p>Just type a broad keyword into the search box.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="949" height="439" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1.png" alt="A Search for Organic Soap on Amazon(1)" class="wp-image-73728" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1.png 949w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-768x355.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-740x342.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon1-1-385x178.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 949px) 100vw, 949px" /></figure></div>



<p>You’ll quickly get a nice list of keyword ideas.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Then repeat for all of the key products on your site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="940" height="443" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1.png" alt="A Search for Organic Soap on Amazon" class="wp-image-73732" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1.png 940w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-300x141.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-768x362.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-380x179.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-600x283.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-760x358.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-106x50.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-740x349.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-220x104.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A-Search-for-Organic-Soap-on-Amazon-1-385x181.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px" /></figure></div>



<p>Another simple trick is to use Google’s related searches features.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Again, type in a broad keyword.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="809" height="173" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1.png" alt="Organic Soap Search Query" class="wp-image-73772" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1.png 809w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-300x64.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-768x164.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-380x81.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-600x128.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-760x163.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-164x35.png 164w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-234x50.png 234w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-740x158.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-220x47.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Soap-Search-Query-1-385x82.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 809px) 100vw, 809px" /></figure></div>



<p>Then scroll down to the bottom to related searches.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="551" height="182" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1.png" alt="Searches Related to Organic Soap" class="wp-image-73796" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1.png 551w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1-300x99.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1-380x126.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1-106x35.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1-151x50.png 151w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1-220x73.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Soap-1-385x127.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 551px) 100vw, 551px" /></figure></div>



<p>This can supply you with even more ideas.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>You can also click on one of the related searches to get even more specific keyword ideas.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="566" height="194" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1.png" alt="Organic Handmade Soap" class="wp-image-73768" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1.png 566w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1-380x130.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1-146x50.png 146w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1-220x75.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Organic-Handmade-Soap-1-385x132.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px" /></figure></div>



<p>Scroll down to the bottom again, and there you go.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="502" height="187" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1.png" alt="Searches Related to Organic Homemade Soap" class="wp-image-73792" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1.png 502w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1-300x112.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1-380x142.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1-94x35.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1-134x50.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1-220x82.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Searches-Related-to-Organic-Homemade-Soap-1-385x143.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 502px) 100vw, 502px" /></figure></div>



<p>Repeat ad infinitum until you have a sizable list of keywords.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>From there you may want to do a bit more investigating to check out details like a keyword’s monthly search volume, difficulty to rank for, and more.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>You can do this with <a href="https://ahrefs.com/keywords-explorer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Ahref’s Keyword Explorer</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="446" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-1024x446.png" alt="Ahrefs Keyword Planner" class="wp-image-73736" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-1024x446.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-768x334.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-380x165.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-600x261.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-760x331.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-740x322.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ahrefs-Keyword-Planner-1.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Generally speaking, your best bet is to stick with long-tail keywords with a minimum of three words.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Being too broad can marginalize your efforts. It’s going to be difficult to eclipse competitors and get out from Amazon’s shadow (unless of course, you perform a <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/competitive-analysis" target="_blank">competitor analysis</a>).<br></p>



<h3><strong>Optimizing Product Pages</strong></h3>



<p>Now it’s time to take your keywords and incorporate them into your product pages.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Doing this involves following many of the same basic SEO principles that you would for any other type of website or blog.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h4><strong>i. URL</strong></h4>



<p>You want to start by creating a short, succinct URL that incorporates your target keyword.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://backlinko.com/on-page-seo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">According to Backlinko</a>, 3-5 words is ideal.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s a good example:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="468" height="32" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1.png" alt="Permalink Example" class="wp-image-73776" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1.png 468w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1-300x21.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1-380x26.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1-180x12.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1-250x17.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1-220x15.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Permalink-Example-1-385x26.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px" /></figure></div>



<h4><strong>ii. H1 Tag</strong></h4>



<p>As you probably already know, header tags (H1s in particular) carry a considerable amount of weight.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>So it only makes sense that you’ll want to include your target keyword in the H1 Tag of your product page.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="405" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-1024x405.png" alt="H1 Tag on Product Page" class="wp-image-73760" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-1024x405.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-300x119.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-768x304.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-380x150.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-600x237.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-760x300.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-89x35.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-126x50.png 126w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-740x293.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-220x87.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1-385x152.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H1-Tag-on-Product-Page-1.png 1194w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h4><strong>iii. Product Descriptions</strong></h4>



<p>To truly get the most out of e-commerce SEO, you want to include some <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">well-crafted copy</a> for each product.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>This helps search engines figure out more details about your product, which should give you an edge in the SERPs.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But here’s the thing. Many e-commerce stores skimp on this area.<br></p>



<p>Many create product descriptions that are too thin or simply feature duplicate content from the manufacturer’s website.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>This, however, is good for you because it provides you with an opportunity to surpass your competitors.<br></p>



<p>By creating robust product descriptions featuring target keywords, you can elevate your overall SEO.<br></p>



<p>In terms of length, there’s still some debate as to what’s ideal. Some experts recommend using up to 300 words.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Others, like Brian Dean, recommend going all out and writing 1,000+ word descriptions.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Dean’s logic is that it helps your customers better understand your product and helps Google understand what your page is about.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Others think that this is overkill when you consider that much of online shopping is done through mobile devices and say that 50-100 words often makes more sense.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Quite honestly, there isn’t an ideal length for product descriptions that works 100 percent of the time.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And it largely depends on the product. For instance, 1,000 words may make sense for a complex electronic product with dozens of features, but would probably be unnecessary for a bar of soap.<br></p>



<p>Therefore, you should use your best judgment.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>At the end of the day, the product description should be thorough enough to answer any pressing questions your customers may have and should incorporate your keywords in a natural manner.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>If you do this, you should be good to go.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<h4><strong>iv. Image Optimization</strong></h4>



<p>There are two steps that go into image optimization.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>First, be sure that at least one of your images contains your target keyword in the file name.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For example, “lemon_rosemary_soap.jpg”.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Second, be sure to include the target keyword as part of your Alt text.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h4><strong>v. Meta-Data</strong></h4>



<p>Just as you would include your target keyword in the meta description on any other page, you’ll want to do this for each product.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>This should be a max of 160 characters in length.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h3><strong>Adding Customer Reviews</strong></h3>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Customer reviews</a> kill two birds with one stone.<br></p>



<p>First, they help you build trust with online shoppers and increase your brand’s credibility.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In fact, “<a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/learn/local-consumer-review-survey-2014/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">88 percent of consumers</a> say that they trust online reviews as much as personal recommendations.”<br></p>



<p>This can ultimately increase your conversions and overall revenue.<br></p>



<p>Second, they provide some additional text that search engines can use to better understand what the content on a particular page is about.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here’s a good example:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-1024x510.png" alt="Customer Reviews Example" class="wp-image-73740" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Customer-Reviews-Example-1.png 1059w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Studies have even found that “reviews can have an <a href="https://webrepublic.com/en/news/blog/infographic-everything-you-need-to-know-about-online-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">impact of up to 10 percent</a> on a business’s search rankings.”<br></p>



<p>Although this may be over the top, every little bit helps. So it’s smart to include a few reviews of your products if at all possible.<br></p>



<p>And you don’t need to go crazy because “40 percent of buyers form an opinion of a business after reading just 1-3 reviews.”</p>



<h3><strong>Social Signals</strong></h3>



<p>While there’s still some debate as to the exact impact that social signals have, you can’t deny that <em>they do affect SEO</em>.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a screenshot of where Brian Dean ranks some of the most common social signals among his top <a href="https://backlinko.com/google-ranking-factors" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">200 Google Ranking Factors</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="577" height="560" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1.png" alt="Most Common Social Signals" class="wp-image-73764" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1.png 577w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-300x291.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-380x369.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-36x35.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-52x50.png 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-505x490.png 505w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-220x214.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Most-Common-Social-Signals-1-385x374.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px" /></figure></div>



<p>So yeah, social signals are kind of a big deal.<br></p>



<p>Following this line of logic, it only makes sense that you would want to incorporate social share buttons into your product pages.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="368" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-1024x368.png" alt="Social Shares on Product Pages" class="wp-image-73820" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-1024x368.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-300x108.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-768x276.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-380x137.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-600x216.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-760x273.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-97x35.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-139x50.png 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-740x266.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-220x79.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1-385x138.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Social-Shares-on-Product-Pages-1.png 1129w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This encourages customers to share your products and provides them a convenient means of doing so.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And in the long run, this can definitely give your e-commerce site more SEO oomph.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h3><strong>Building Internal Links</strong></h3>



<p>You’re probably already aware of the value that internal links can have on a regular website or blog.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Brian Dean even lists the number of internal links and the quality of internal links as numbers 38 and 39 on his top 200 Google ranking factors.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>This same concept applies to an e-commerce store.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>So make it a point to look for internal linking opportunities where you link from authoritative pages to your top priority product pages.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Also, be sure that you’re using keyword rich anchor text when doing so.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Check out <a href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/what-is-anchor-text-and-how-can-i-optimize-it/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">this resource from SEMrush</a> for more on anchor text optimization.<br></p>



<h3><strong>Addressing Security&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Online security is a huge deal these days.<br></p>



<p>Every single day more than <a href="http://breachlevelindex.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">five million data records</a> are lost or stolen, which equates to 59 records every second.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="319" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-1024x319.png" alt="Data Records Are Lost or Stolen at The Following Frequency" class="wp-image-73744" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-1024x319.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-300x94.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-768x240.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-380x119.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-600x187.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-760x237.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-112x35.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-160x50.png 160w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-740x231.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-220x69.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1-385x120.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Data-Records-Are-Lost-or-Stolen-at-The-Following-Frequency-1.png 1183w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>So it should come as no surprise that Google now considers security to be a ranking factor.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>More specifically, <a href="https://security.googleblog.com/2014/08/https-as-ranking-signal_6.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">HTTPS is a ranking signal</a> meaning that you want to switch from HTTP to HTTPs if you haven’t done so already.<br></p>



<p>This is done by obtaining a secure socket layer (SSL) certificate, which you can <a href="https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/6033049?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=6033084" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">learn about here</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Making this move is pretty much a necessity in this day and age.<br></p>



<p>Not only does it help protect the sensitive information of your customers, it makes your e-commerce site look more legitimate in the eyes of search engines.&nbsp;<br></p>



<h3><strong>Revving Up Your Site Speed</strong></h3>



<p>This is a biggie, and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/page-load-time" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">page loading speed</a> is even listed at number 20 in the top 200 Google Ranking Factors.<br></p>



<p>Even if you have an amazing e-commerce site that’s optimized to perfection, your success will be marginalized if it’s painfully slow.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here are a few stats that show just how critical this really is from a customer satisfaction standpoint:<br></p>



<ul><li>47 percent of consumers expect a web page to load in two seconds or less.</li><li>40 percent abandon websites that take more than three seconds to load.</li><li>79 percent of shoppers who are dissatisfied with website performance are less likely to buy from the same site again.&nbsp;</li><li>As little as a one second delay decreases customer satisfaction by about 16 percent.</li></ul>



<p>The bottom line is that having a fast loading site is important for SEO and for pleasing your customers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>So how do you speed it up?<br></p>



<p>First, use the <a href="https://tools.pingdom.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pingdom Website Speed Test</a> to determine just how fast your site is and how it compares with similar sites.<br></p>



<p>Simply enter your URL and start the test.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="941" height="246" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1.png" alt="Pingdom Website Speed" class="wp-image-73788" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1.png 941w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-300x78.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-768x201.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-380x99.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-600x157.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-760x199.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-134x35.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-191x50.png 191w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-740x193.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-220x58.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-1-385x101.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 941px) 100vw, 941px" /></figure></div>



<p>From there, your site will be graded, and you’ll receive some specific performance insights.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="518" height="202" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1.png" alt="Pingdom Website Speed Results" class="wp-image-73784" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1.png 518w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1-300x117.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1-380x148.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1-90x35.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1-128x50.png 128w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1-220x86.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Website-Speed-Results-1-385x150.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="806" height="467" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1.png" alt="Pingdom Performance Insights" class="wp-image-73780" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1.png 806w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-768x445.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-380x220.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-600x348.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-760x440.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-740x429.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pingdom-Performance-Insights-1-385x223.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 806px) 100vw, 806px" /></figure></div>



<p>Then use this information to identify which specific areas you need to address in order to speed up your site.&nbsp;<br></p>


