<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Model This Black Friday Marketing Strategy for Your Next Holiday Campaign</strong></h2>



<p>It’s no secret that <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Black Friday</a> is one of the busiest times of the year for any e-retailer…<br></p>



<p>And it’s one of the most profitable.<br></p>



<p>In fact, <a href="https://www.finder.com/black-friday-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">according to one recent report</a>, the average adult drops <strong>$483.18</strong> on Black Friday and Cyber Monday alone.<br></p>



<p>So, it’s no surprise then, that many online stores—Bellroy included—get creative with their Black Friday marketing come holiday season.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>While writing this post, I saw a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/facebook-lead-ads" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Facebook lead ad</a> from Bellroy teasing a subscriber-exclusive promotion they were running for Black Friday.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="198" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad.jpg" alt="Bellroy_s Black Friday Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-78979" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad-300x99.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad-380x125.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad-106x35.jpg 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad-152x50.jpg 152w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad-220x73.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Facebook-Ad-385x127.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I clicked on the ad, Bellroy redirected me to a dedicated landing page, promoting a “Black Friday Subscriber Exclusive.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-1024x491.png" alt="Bellroy_s Black Friday Landing Page" class="wp-image-78983" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Landing-Page.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In their copy, they opened a curiosity gap by teasing a one-day only promotion. Here’s an excerpt:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="620" height="180" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy.png" alt="Bellroy_s Black Friday Teaser Copy" class="wp-image-78987" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy.png 620w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-300x87.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-380x110.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-600x174.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-121x35.png 121w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-172x50.png 172w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-220x64.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Teaser-Copy-385x112.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></figure></div>



<p>After entering my email address, I got an email with the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">subject line</a>, “Psst. Don’t miss our Black Friday gift.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="930" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email.png" alt="Bellroy_s Black Friday Email" class="wp-image-78975" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-194x300.png 194w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-380x589.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-23x35.png 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-32x50.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-316x490.png 316w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-220x341.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-385x597.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>A day later—incidentally, on Black Friday—I got another email with the subject line, “Your Black Friday gift awaits—don’t let it disappear.”<br></p>



<p>There are a few things going in their email that are worth highlighting:<br></p>



<ol><li>Animation;</li><li>Copy; and</li><li>User experience.</li></ol>



<p>Let’s look at each briefly.<br></p>





<h3><strong>i. Animation</strong></h3>



<p>Bellroy has become known for their use of visuals on their product pages. And, as luck would have it, their emails are no exception.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Take their Black Friday email, for example. In it, Bellroy included a GIF that flashed up the amount of credit they were offering for multiple currencies.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="586" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-Credit-is-Waiting.gif" alt="Your Credit is Waiting" class="wp-image-79095"/></figure></div>



<p>One reason they might have done this was to ensure that all readers could relate to the offer.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For instance, if you’re American, $24 Australian Dollars (AUD) is harder to grasp than if it were in American Dollars (USD). Without a frame of reference for another country’s currency, it’s difficult to know whether you’re getting a good deal, meaning you’re unlikely to take action.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>To remove any ambiguity, Bellroy cleverly frame their offer for each currency they accept to make it easier for potential buyers to relate to (and hopefully, take action on).&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Interestingly, it’s not just in their emails that they’re doing this; it’s in certain display ads too.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="775" height="700" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1.png" alt="Bellroy Google Display Ad 2" class="wp-image-79103" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1.png 775w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-300x271.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-768x694.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-380x343.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-600x542.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-760x686.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-55x50.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-543x490.png 543w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-220x199.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-2-1-385x348.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></figure></div>



<p>Framing is everything. Don’t leave it to chance.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Use GIFs to grab readers’ attention, and promote offers in multiple currencies.</p>
</div></div>





<h3><strong>ii. Copy</strong></h3>



<p>Bellroy’s Black Friday email has great copy. But there’s one section worth highlighting more than any other.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Beneath the GIF we looked at above, Bellroy writes&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="655" height="225" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2.png" alt="P.S. in Bellroy Black Friday Marketing Email 2" class="wp-image-79059" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2.png 655w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-380x131.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-600x206.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-146x50.png 146w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy-Black-Friday-Marketing-Email-2-385x132.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 655px) 100vw, 655px" /></figure></div>



<p>And it’s clever, because Bellroy create urgency to justify <em>why</em> they’re running the promotion, and it gives us a compelling reason to make a purchase.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="editors-note-block_5f6df05aa619d" class="block-editors-note">
    <h3>Editor&#8217;s Note</h3>
    <div><p>It’s worth mentioning here that giving a reason for a discount—any reason, for that matter—is always better than omitting one (even if the reason is obvious). To learn more about discount strategies, read Rikke’s article, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">9 Discount Strategies You Can Use Today (Without Hurting Sales)</a>.</p>
</div>
    <div class="author">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Sam-120x120.png" width="120" height="120" alt="Sam Thomas Davies" class="avatar avatar-120 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-120 alignnone photo" /><div class="author-data"><div class="name">Sam Thomas Davies</div><div class="title">Head of Content</div></div>    </div>
</div>








<p>After Bellroy justify why they’re running the promotion, they explain how the offer works:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="655" height="330" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works.png" alt="How It Works" class="wp-image-79031" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works.png 655w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-300x151.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-380x191.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-600x302.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-99x50.png 99w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-220x111.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/How-It-Works-385x194.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 655px) 100vw, 655px" /></figure></div>



<p>And it leaves nothing to the reader’s imagination.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Beneath these three statements is a P.S., where Bellroy invite readers NOT to forward the email to friends, knowing, of course, that this is exactly what will likely happen.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-1024x167.png" alt="P.S. in Bellroy_s Black Friday Email" class="wp-image-79063" width="580" height="94" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-1024x167.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-300x49.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-768x125.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-380x62.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-600x98.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-760x124.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-180x29.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-250x41.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-740x120.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-220x36.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-385x63.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/P.S.-in-Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email.png 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Bellroy’s playful use of reverse psychology in their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email copy</a>.&nbsp;</em></p>





<p>Much like little hinges swing big doors, micro-tweaks to your copy move more orders. Don’t leave it to chance.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> When running a promotion, explain how readers can claim their offer, step-by-step, to reduce confusion. Bonus: think about how you can encourage referrals. You don’t have to use reverse psychology like Bellroy does in their P.S., but it might help.<br></p>





<h3><strong>iii. User-Experience</strong></h3>



<p>After explaining how readers can claim their Black Friday discount, Bellroy includes a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> (CTA) in the email.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="456" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-1024x456.png" alt="Shop Now" class="wp-image-79071" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-1024x456.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-768x342.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-760x338.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-740x329.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now-385x171.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Shop-Now.png 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I clicked “Shop Now,” Bellroy auto-applied my credit (much like how <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/meundies-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">MeUndies</a> do for listeners coming from their podcast sponsorships).&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="948" height="426" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA.png" alt="Bellroy_s Black Friday Email CTA" class="wp-image-78971" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA.png 948w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-768x345.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Black-Friday-Email-CTA-385x173.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 948px) 100vw, 948px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I added an item to my cart and checked out, Bellroy deducted €15 and showed me how much I’d saved. (Note: Bellroy chose Euros as my preferred currency because I’m in Sweden and they don’t accept Swedish Krona.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="765" height="375" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout.png" alt="Bellroy_s Checkout" class="wp-image-78991" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout.png 765w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-380x186.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-600x294.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-760x373.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-740x363.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Checkout-385x189.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 765px) 100vw, 765px" /></figure></div>



<p>While their competitors bombard their visitors with Black Friday reminders, Bellroy creates <em>exclusivity</em>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Buying discounted goods from them was a right reserved ONLY for email subscribers. In fact, when I tried to get a discount ON Black Friday, after pretending I wasn’t on their list, Bellroy said no (and rightfully so).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="750" height="422" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat.png" alt="Bellroy Live Chat" class="wp-image-78951" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat.png 750w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Live-Chat-385x217.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></figure></div>



<p>What I love about Bellroy’s strategy is that it isn’t limited to Black Friday. You can use it for ANY holiday. Christmas. Easter. Martin Luther King Day. You name it. The possibilities are endless. Get moving.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Generate demand for holiday promotions BEFORE you need it. Drive traffic to a dedicated landing page, <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank">grow your list</a>, create as much buzz as possible, and then give your buyers the exclusivity they deserve.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Use “The Life Force 8” to Maximize Ad Conversions</strong></h2>



<p>There are two things you need to know about Bellroy’s marketing strategy.<br></p>



<p>One, <strong>23.80%</strong> of their overall desktop traffic comes from display ads.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="343" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-1024x343.png" alt="Bellroy_s Traffic Sources" class="wp-image-79015" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-1024x343.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-300x100.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-768x257.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-380x127.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-600x201.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-760x254.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-105x35.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-149x50.png 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-740x248.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-220x74.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources-385x129.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Sources.png 1390w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And two, they leverage three marketing angles in their ad copy.<br></p>



<p>But it’s not just any three marketing angles— these are angles that build on what are known as <em>The Life Force 8.</em><br></p>



<p>In his book, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/CA-HVERTISING-Ad-Agency-Psychology-Anything/dp/1601630328/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>Cashvertising</em></a>, Drew Eric Whitman outlines eight biological desires we all have:<br></p>



<ol><li>Survival, enjoyment of life, life extension;</li><li>Enjoyment of food and beverages;</li><li>Freedom from fear, pain, and danger;</li><li>Sexual companionship;</li><li>Comfortable living conditions;</li><li>Being superior, winning, keeping up with the Joneses;</li><li>Care and protection of loved ones; and</li><li>Social approval.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol>



<p>Bellroy appeals to three of the above angles in many of their top-converting display ads.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Let’s look at each briefly.<br></p>





<h3><strong>1. Being Superior, Winning, Keeping up with the Joneses</strong></h3>



<p>To all intents and purposes, Bellroy’s core offer is slim leather wallets for men. And after browsing their site for a few minutes, it’s hard to argue otherwise.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But when you take a look at their paid advertising, it’s clear that they’re marketing to a segment <em>within</em> that segment. Specifically, <em>fashion-conscious marketing executives.</em><br></p>



<p>Why?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><strong>Because, generally, it’s a market segment that can and will happily pay more to fulfill the above innate desire to be superior.&nbsp;</strong><br></p>



<p>You can see Bellroy appealing to superiority in ad copy, from inviting buyers to “Look the part&#8230;”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="726" height="88" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part.png" alt="Look the Part" class="wp-image-79055" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part.png 726w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-300x36.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-380x46.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-600x73.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-180x22.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-250x30.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-220x27.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Look-the-Part-385x47.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 726px) 100vw, 726px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;to naming the product itself “The Executive Wallet.”&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="127" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-1024x127.png" alt="The Executive Wallet" class="wp-image-79087" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-1024x127.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-300x37.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-768x95.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-380x47.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-600x74.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-760x94.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-1440x178.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-180x22.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-250x31.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-740x91.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-220x27.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet-385x48.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Executive-Wallet.png 1456w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Interestingly, the products Bellroy promote in the above ads and other similar ones, are also some of their more high-end items. Coincidence? Maybe. But with ad copy like the above, it’s hard to disagree with.<br></p>





<h3><strong>2. Freedom from Fear, Pain, and Danger</strong></h3>



<p>“Positioning is not about creating something new and different,” write Al Ries and Jack Trout in their book, <em>Positioning</em>. “It’s about manipulating what’s already in the prospect’s mind. It’s about bridging the connections that already exist.”<br></p>



<p>One thing that’s in the mind of a Bellroy customer is the fear of losing their valuables when travelling.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Bellroy recognizes that, and with the information in mind, position their travel collection as a remedy to that fear in many of their ads.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="968" height="242" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign.png" alt="Bellroy Google Search Campaign" class="wp-image-78943" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign.png 968w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-300x75.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-768x192.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-380x95.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-600x150.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-760x190.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-140x35.png 140w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-200x50.png 200w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-740x185.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-220x55.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Search-Campaign-385x96.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 968px) 100vw, 968px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you click “Learn More,” Bellroy redirect you to a product page with copy that reassures and reiterates the above solution.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="740" height="475" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection.png" alt="The Travel Collection" class="wp-image-79091" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-300x193.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-380x244.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-600x385.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-78x50.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-220x141.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/The-Travel-Collection-385x247.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px" /></figure></div>



<p>Not only are they following best practice in terms of message matching (i.e. ensuring their messaging is consistent, from their ads to their landing pages); but they’re also freeing their customers from pain, while positioning their product as a solution in the process.&nbsp;<br></p>





<h3><strong>3. Care and Protection of Loved Ones</strong></h3>



<p>Have you ever regretted making a purchase? Of course you have. You’re not alone; we’re all guilty of it from time to time. Buyer’s remorse, as it’s known, is very real. Oftentimes, we buy something expensive only to convince ourselves later that we shouldn’t have bought it.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what if your purchase benefited a cause greater than yourself? How would you rationalize it then?<br></p>



<p>While researching this post, I saw an interesting Facebook carousel ad from Bellroy. Take a look at the ad copy:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="624" height="691" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad.png" alt="Bellroy Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-78923" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad.png 624w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-271x300.png 271w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-380x421.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-600x664.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-442x490.png 442w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-220x244.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Facebook-Ad-385x426.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px" /></figure></div>



<p>Knowing that caring and protecting loved ones is an innate emotional trigger, Bellroy frames their offer as benefiting <em>others</em> rather than the individual. How? With the sentiment, “Helping yourself helps others, too.”&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>“Need we go on?” they ask.<br></p>



<p>No. That’s as good a reason as any to buy.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Use one or several of the above Life Force 8 angles to inspire marketing angles in your paid advertising. Pro tip: use Facebook’s Dynamic Creative to test different angles against one another.</p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. The Marketer Magnet Method: How to Rank a Product Page Position #3</strong></h2>



<p>Using a tool like <a href="https://ahrefs.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Ahrefs</a>, we can see that Bellroy ranks for several high-volume commercial-intent keywords. But the one I want to focus on here is the keyword “slim wallet.”<br></p>



<p>At the time of writing, Bellroy ranks position #3 for that term. But they also have a whopping 396 domains linking to the relevant product page (339 of which are do-follow).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="925" height="380" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page.png" alt="Links to Bellroy_s Slim Your Wallet Product Page" class="wp-image-79051" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page.png 925w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-300x123.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-768x316.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-380x156.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-600x246.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-760x312.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-85x35.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-122x50.png 122w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-740x304.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-220x90.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Links-to-Bellroy_s-Slim-Your-Wallet-Product-Page-385x158.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 925px) 100vw, 925px" /></figure></div>



<p>How are they doing it?<br></p>



<p>Well, one approach, intentional or not, is what I call “The Marketer Magnet Method.”<br></p>



<p>I’ve written about it before, but it bears repeating because there are NO limits to its usage.<br></p>



<p>As a reminder, <strong>“The Marketer Magnet Method” involves approaching marketing in such an interesting way that marketing blogs can’t help but link to you.</strong><br></p>



<p>(Yes, I’m aware that’s exactly what I’m doing now. Pretty meta, huh?)<br></p>



<p>It might be using a quiz to turn visitors into buyers, like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/beardbrand-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Beardbrand</a>. Or using a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/thank-you-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">thank you page</a> to survey visitors, like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Harry’s</a>.<br></p>



<p>But that’s only the beginning.<br></p>



<p>Bellroy has links from authority sites for many aspects of their marketing—including ones you might not have considered.<br></p>



<p>Take their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/above-the-fold-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">above-the-fold content</a>, for instance.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Unlike their competitors, who highlight their products’ benefits through images, Bellroy goes a step further and <em>shows</em> their products’ value using an interactive slider.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-1024x640.gif" alt="Slim Your Wallet" class="wp-image-79075" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-1024x640.gif 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-300x188.gif 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-768x480.gif 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-1536x960.gif 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-380x238.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-600x375.gif 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-760x475.gif 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-1440x900.gif 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-56x35.gif 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-80x50.gif 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-740x463.gif 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-220x138.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Slim-Your-Wallet-385x241.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Many marketing blogs have praised Bellroy for it, including giants like <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/product-pages-love-list" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">HubSpot</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="760" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy.png" alt="HubSpot Link to Bellroy" class="wp-image-79035" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-300x253.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-380x320.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-600x505.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-59x50.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-582x490.png 582w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-220x185.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/HubSpot-Link-to-Bellroy-385x324.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px" /></figure></div>



<p>But it doesn’t stop there.<br></p>



<p>Whether it’s how they’re using animation in their explainer videos (Source: <a href="https://econsultancy.com/21-examples-of-user-experience-innovation-in-ecommerce/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Smashing Magazine</a>)&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="880" height="665" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine.png" alt="Link to Bellroy from Smashing Magazine" class="wp-image-79047" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine.png 880w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-300x227.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-768x580.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-380x287.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-600x453.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-760x574.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-66x50.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-648x490.png 648w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-220x166.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Smashing-Magazine-385x291.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;how they’re being innovative with the user experience (Source: <a href="https://econsultancy.com/25-excellent-ux-examples-from-ecommerce-sites/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">eConsultancy</a>)&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="900" height="802" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy.png" alt="eConsultancy Link to Bellroy" class="wp-image-79023" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy.png 900w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-300x267.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-768x684.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-380x339.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-600x535.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-760x677.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-56x50.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-550x490.png 550w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-220x196.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/eConsultancy-Link-to-Bellroy-385x343.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;or even how they’re using scrolling on their site (<a href="https://www.hongkiat.com/blog/web-design-scrolling/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Hongkiat</a>)&#8230;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="469" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-1024x469.png" alt="Hongkiat Link to Bellroy" class="wp-image-79027" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-1024x469.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-300x137.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-1536x704.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-760x348.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-1440x660.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy-385x176.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Hongkiat-Link-to-Bellroy.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Bellroy has earned their fair share of backlinks for marketing that is <em>so </em>original, marketers can’t help but write about it.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Take a look at your marketing. What are you doing that’s original or uncommon in your industry? We grew tired of seeing GIFs in marketing emails, so we created our own. Marketers took notice, and we got a few links for doing so. Don’t get discouraged if you’re a small business; standing out is often easier than you think.</p>




