<h2 id="4"><strong>4. How to Market to the Affluent (Hint: It Doesn’t Involve More Ad Spends)</strong></h2>



<p>It’s always interesting to see how big brands use their email footers.<br></p>



<p>It’s prime email real estate after all, and it shouldn’t be wasted (though if often is.)<br></p>



<p>While writing this post, Bellroy’s email footer caught my attention because they’re doing something I haven’t seen before.<br></p>



<p>Take a recent promotional email I received. In it, Bellroy had many calls-to-action (CTAs). But there was one that caught my attention more than any other.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="246" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-1024x246.png" alt="Reward Your Team" class="wp-image-79107" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-1024x246.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-300x72.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-768x185.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-380x91.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-600x144.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-760x183.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-145x35.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-208x50.png 208w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-740x178.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1-385x93.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Reward-Your-Team-1.png 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I clicked the link, Bellroy redirected me to a dedicated landing page, promoting “Gifts for Staff and Clients”:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-1024x491.png" alt="Bellroy_s Gifts for Staff and Clients" class="wp-image-78999" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Gifts-for-Staff-and-Clients.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>On it, their copy says,<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="272" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-1024x272.png" alt="Your People Are Important to You" class="wp-image-79099" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-1024x272.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-768x204.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-1536x408.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-380x101.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-600x159.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-760x202.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-1440x383.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-132x35.png 132w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-188x50.png 188w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-740x197.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-220x58.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You-385x102.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Your-People-Are-Important-to-You.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s clever, for two reasons:<br></p>



<ol><li><strong>It plays on another marketing angle: social approval.</strong> If you think about it, Bellroy isn&#8217;t selling to you. They’re not appealing to how their products will benefit <em>you</em> personally. Instead, they’re appealing to how their products will benefit those <em>around</em> you—and imply what that will mean for you.</li><li><strong>Corporate gifting is a clever upsell for their buyer persona.</strong> As mentioned above, Bellroy market to business executives in their paid advertising. And corporate gifting—including monograms or embossed logos, initials or custom messages—is an easy (yet highly lucrative) upsell for that market segment.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol>



<p>After enquiring to find out more, I got a confirmation email…<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="895" height="475" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program.png" alt="Thanks for Reaching Out About Our Corporate Sales Program" class="wp-image-79083" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program.png 895w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-300x159.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-768x408.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-380x202.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-600x318.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-760x403.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-66x35.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-94x50.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-740x393.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-220x117.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Thanks-for-Reaching-Out-About-Our-Corporate-Sales-Program-385x204.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 895px) 100vw, 895px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;followed by an email from a sales representative a day later:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1025" height="415" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email.png" alt="Bellroy Corporate Gifting Sales Email" class="wp-image-78919" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email.png 1025w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-300x121.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-768x311.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-380x154.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-600x243.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-760x308.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-86x35.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-123x50.png 123w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-740x300.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-220x89.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Corporate-Gifting-Sales-Email-385x156.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1025px) 100vw, 1025px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s hard to know why Bellroy offer corporate gifting through email only, it’s likely that it’s more personalized and easier to match an offer to the buyer’s needs.<br></p>



<p>It’s also easy to follow up on, which, judging from the prompt I got when I didn’t reply, is a big part of their sales process.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="212" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-1024x212.png" alt="Bellroy Follow Up Email" class="wp-image-78927" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-1024x212.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-300x62.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-768x159.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-380x79.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-600x124.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-760x158.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-169x35.png 169w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-241x50.png 241w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-740x153.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-220x46.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email-385x80.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Follow-Up-Email.png 1230w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Interestingly, when I <em>did</em> reply, I learned more about what they offer. And as you can see from the excerpt below, there’s a lot of opportunity for Bellroy to upsell to their corporate customers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="183" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-1024x183.png" alt="Some Thoughts Re. Gift Ideas for Each of Your Team Members" class="wp-image-79079" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-1024x183.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-300x54.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-768x137.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-1536x275.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-380x68.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-600x107.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-760x136.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-1440x257.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-180x32.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-250x45.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-740x132.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-220x39.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members-385x69.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Some-Thoughts-Re.-Gift-Ideas-for-Each-of-Your-Team-Members.png 1790w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Granted, corporate gifting isn’t for everyone. But if a segment of your target market is business executives, it’s a great way to scale your business.</p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Translate Your Site to Expand Your Reach</strong></h2>



<p>Like any fast-growing e-tailer, Bellroy knows which countries are driving the most traffic to their site.<br></p>



<p>In fact, by using a tool like <a href="http://similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SimilarWeb</a>, we can see that the majority of Bellroy’s traffic comes from the United States, the United Kingdom, and their native Australia.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="920" height="380" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1.png" alt="Bellroy_s Traffic Share by Country(1)" class="wp-image-79007" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1.png 920w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-300x124.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-768x317.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-380x157.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-600x248.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-760x314.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-85x35.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-121x50.png 121w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-740x306.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-220x91.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country1-385x159.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, it makes sense that Bellroy advertises to those countries’ users in English. After all, English is the mother tongue for each of those countries.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what about countries like Germany—and even certain regions in Canada—where English isn’t the first language?<br></p>



<p>If we take a closer look at Bellroy’s marketing, we can see that they’re growing their market share in other countries by translating their ads—and their site copy—into each country’s first language.<br></p>



<p>Take Germany, for example. In the past 30 days, Bellroy has seen a 104.8% increase in traffic.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="228" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-1024x228.png" alt="Bellroy_s Traffic Share by Country" class="wp-image-79011" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-1024x228.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-300x67.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-768x171.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-380x84.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-600x133.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-760x169.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-157x35.png 157w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-225x50.png 225w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-740x165.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-220x49.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country-385x86.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Traffic-Share-by-Country.png 1309w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, it makes perfect sense to have German ads…<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="672" height="560" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1.png" alt="Bellroy German Ad" class="wp-image-79111" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1.png 672w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-300x250.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-380x317.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-600x500.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-588x490.png 588w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-220x183.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-German-Ad-1-385x321.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;and landing page copy.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-1024x491.png" alt="Bellroy_s German Subdomain" class="wp-image-78995" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-German-Subdomain.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Translating ad and landing page copy into a target market’s language personalizes your marketing—and it’s a great way to welcome new website visitors.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Log into Google Analytics and click, “Audience &gt; Overview &gt; Country” to identify your audience by country. Then, consider translating your ad copy into the mother tongue of one or more of those target countries.</p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Recruit Partners to Grow Your Customer Base</strong></h2>



<p>Whether it’s co-creating an offer or promoting another company’s products or services, strategic partnerships are a great way to tap into new markets.<br></p>



<p>One way Bellroy has grown their reach in recent years is by partnering with brands in similar verticals—particularly those with a wider reach than Bellroy.<br></p>



<p>Take online retailer <a href="https://huckberry.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Huckberry</a>, for instance.<br></p>



<p>They loved Bellroy’s Hide &amp; Seek wallet so much that they asked Bellroy to make them one of their own.&nbsp;<br></p>



<iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHuckberry%2Fposts%2F1064278503583025&amp;width=600&amp;show_text=true&amp;appId=681895145242818&amp;height=577" width="600" height="577" style="border:none;overflow:hidden" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>



<p>And unsurprisingly, due to its limited availability, it flew off the digital shelves. (Note the dual branding on the wallet).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-1024x640.png" alt="Huckberry Hide and Seek" class="wp-image-79039" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Hide-and-Seek.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Huckberry’s collaboration with Bellroy was so successful that they now sell Bellroy products on their site, permanently.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="526" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-1024x526.png" alt="Bellroy on Huckberry" class="wp-image-78967" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-1024x526.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-300x154.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-768x395.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-1536x789.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-380x195.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-600x308.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-760x390.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-1440x740.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-740x380.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry-385x198.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-on-Huckberry.png 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>What started as a one-time collaboration became a long-term partnership benefiting both brands.</em></p>





<p>More recently, Bellroy partnered with Google to develop a sleeve for Google’s Pixelbook.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="526" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-1024x526.png" alt="Bellroy_s Pixelbook Sleeve" class="wp-image-79003" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-1024x526.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-300x154.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-768x395.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-1536x789.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-380x195.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-600x308.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-760x390.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-1440x740.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-740x380.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve-385x198.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Pixelbook-Sleeve.png 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The best part? Not only was it good <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">social proof</a> for Bellroy, they also got a TON of free press from several authority review blogs.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="475" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-1024x475.png" alt="Bellroy in Google News" class="wp-image-78947" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-1024x475.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-768x356.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-1536x713.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-760x353.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-1440x668.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-740x343.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-in-Google-News.png 1950w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Even better, they got a nice do-follow link from the <a href="https://store.google.com/us/product/bellroy_pixelbook_sleeve" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Google Store</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="152" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-1024x152.png" alt="Link to Bellroy from Google Store" class="wp-image-79043" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-1024x152.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-300x45.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-768x114.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-1536x229.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-380x57.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-600x89.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-760x113.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-1440x214.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-180x27.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-740x110.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-220x33.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store-385x57.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Link-to-Bellroy-from-Google-Store.png 1545w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Granted, not everyone will land the chance to partner with a giant like Google. But it does show the power of partnering in today’s uber-competitive marketplace.<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Action item.</strong> Partnering with other global brands has obvious payoffs—reaching new marketers, free publicity, etc. But there are other benefits, like getting links from authority domains, which are often overlooked. If you have a custom-made product, consider partnering with brands in similar verticals to reach new customers.</p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. PAS + BAB = More Conversions&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>As we’ve seen, Bellroy are the masters of visual marketing. But that doesn’t mean they neglect compelling copy to position their products as the best on the market. On closer inspection, Bellroy actually use two proven copywriting formulas in much of their marketing:<br></p>



<ol><li>PAS; and</li><li>BAB</li></ol>



<p>Let’s look at each in more detail.<br></p>





<h3><strong>1. The PAS Formula</strong></h3>



<p>Problem. Agitation. Solution.<br></p>



<p>Once called “<em>the </em>most reliable sales formula ever invented,” by <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/copywriting-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">copywriting</a> legend Dan Kennedy, Problem, Agitation, Solution (or PAS) involves:<br></p>



<ol><li>Defining a prospect’s <strong>problem</strong> and eliciting agreement to inject emotion;</li><li><strong>Agitating</strong> the reader’s emotional responses to that problem; and</li><li>Unveiling the <strong>solution</strong>, which is your products or services and their accompanying benefits.</li></ol>



<p>Bellroy does a wonderful job of using the PAS formula, but my favorite example is in their homepage copy.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Beneath the fold, they position their product in three succinct sentences:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="397" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1024x397.png" alt="Bellroy_s Value Proposition" class="wp-image-79019" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1024x397.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-300x116.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-768x298.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-380x147.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-600x233.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-760x295.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-1440x559.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-90x35.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-129x50.png 129w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-740x287.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-220x85.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition-385x149.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy_s-Value-Proposition.png 1534w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>First, they introduce their prospect’s problem:<br></p>



<p><em>You can get weighed down by baggage, bulk, stuff.</em><br></p>



<p>Then they agitate it, explaining what having that problem means:<br></p>



<p><em>It can slow you down and narrow your view.</em><br></p>



<p>Finally, they position their products as the solution to that problem:<br></p>



<p><em>Bellroy products are designed to make your life easier, smarter and more seamless.</em><br></p>



<p>When you look at a killer value proposition like the above in terms of the building blocks it&#8217;s made from, it’s easy to see why it works—and you can then construct one of your own.<br></p>





<h3><strong>2. The BAB Formula</strong></h3>



<p>If you’re a seasoned copywriter, it’s likely you’re familiar with the Before, After, Bridge (BAB) formula.<br></p>



<p>If not, the BAB formula involves:<br></p>



<ol><li>Conveying an everyday problem that your prospect encounters;</li><li>Introducing a solution; and</li><li>Bridging the before and after with your products or services.&nbsp;</li></ol>



<p>What’s interesting about Bellroy is that rather than using the BAB formula in their copy, they use it in their design assets. Most notably, it’s in their Instagram posts and their Adwords creative.<br></p>



<p>Let’s take a quick look.<br></p>



<p>i. Instagram<br></p>



<p>Many of Bellroy’s Instagram posts emphasize the before and after of using their products. From durability…<br></p>



<blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/BqJ2sYQljW6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="12" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BqJ2sYQljW6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; width:100%;" target="_blank"> <div style=" display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div> <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div> <div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.