.831,79.965 532.853,80.001 541,80.001 C549.148,80.001 550.169,79.965 553.369,79.82 C556.562,79.673 558.743,79.167 560.652,78.425 C562.623,77.658 564.297,76.634 565.965,74.965 C567.633,73.296 568.659,71.625 569.425,69.651 C570.167,67.743 570.674,65.562 570.82,62.369 C570.966,59.17 571,58.147 571,50 C571,41.851 570.966,40.831 570.82,37.631"></path></g></g></g></svg></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"> <div style=" color:#3897f0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:550; line-height:18px;"> View this post on Instagram</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div> <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div> <div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg)"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"> <div style=" width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div> <div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div></a> <p style=" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BhtgbACnj79/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;" target="_blank">Sitting on a burger wallet is a downright pain in the… lower back. But we think burgers are better on plates than in pockets. That wallet on the right is holding the same number of cards as the burger on the left. But it won&#8217;t leave you sitting on a tilt. Slide across to see them in action.</a></p> <p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;">A post shared by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bellroy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;" target="_blank"> Bellroy</a> (@bellroy) on <time style=" font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;" datetime="2018-04-18T12:01:23+00:00">Apr 18, 2018 at 5:01am PDT</time></p></div></blockquote> <script async="" src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script>



<p>&#8230;each image tells a story.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>You’re on the left (before), but after seeing the image, you want to be on the right (after). In their imagery, Bellroy imply, “Our product will bridge the gap between when you are now and where you want to go. We’ll help you do that.”<br></p>



<p>ii. Google Adwords<br></p>



<p>Bellroy employs a similar approach in their Google Adwords creative.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For instance, in the below ad, they cleverly invite you to go from a bulky “Burger” wallet “to a Bellroy.” (Note the cross and checkmark.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="95" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-1024x95.png" alt="Bellroy Google Display Ad" class="wp-image-78939" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-1024x95.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-300x28.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-768x71.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-1536x143.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-380x35.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-600x56.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-760x71.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-1440x134.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-180x17.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-250x23.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-740x69.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-220x20.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad-385x36.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bellroy-Google-Display-Ad.png 1940w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The genius in marketing like this in particular, lies in lampooning the before to such an extent that the reader almost feels embarrassed to be associated with it. They’re then more likely to want to do something about it.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Use copywriting formulas like PAS and BAB to simplify your value proposition and position your product in a way that’s easy for prospects to relate to.</p>




